Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克的心脏比正常人要大三倍\N{\rEnglish}Michael's heart is approximately three times larger than normal size.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\rEnglish}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听不懂\N{\rEnglish}I didn't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:18:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能说简单一点\N{\rEnglish}Could you put that in layman terms for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基本上...\N{\rEnglish}Basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克的心脏无法抽取足够血液...\N{\rEnglish}There's not enough blood being pumped by Michael's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以血液会回流到肺部 逐渐堆积在里面\N{\rEnglish}so it backs up in the lungs like a sponge getting wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的心脏很努力  但徒劳无功\N{\rEnglish}His heart is trying, but it's working too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他需要什么  手术吗?\N{\rEnglish}What does he need, an operation or?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的心脏需要的不是一般手术\N{\rEnglish}We're considerably beyond corrective surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的心脏毫无功用\N{\rEnglish}Mike's heart is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他需要心脏移植  否则就完了\N{\rEnglish}He needs a transplant, or he'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  还有别的选择\N{\rEnglish}Wait a second. There are other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么选择?\N{\rEnglish}What options?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺其自然  用药物治疗他\N{\rEnglish}To do nothing. Medicate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽量让他过的舒适一点\N{\rEnglish}Make him as comfortable as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细考虑生活品质\N{\rEnglish}You'll have to think about quality of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂\N{\rEnglish}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他原来还好好的\N{\rEnglish}We were just with him and he seemed fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他看起来还是会很好\N{\rEnglish}He's going to seem fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但随着他的心脏恶化\N{\rEnglish}But as his heart gets worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会变得越来越累\N{\rEnglish}he'll become increasingly fatigued.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也会越睡越多\N{\rEnglish}And he will sleep more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天他会睡着...\N{\rEnglish}Until one day he will fall asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后不再醒来\N{\rEnglish}and he won't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这很困难...\N{\rEnglish}I know this is difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你们必须面对事实\N{\rEnglish}but you have to face the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的儿子可能活不久\N{\rEnglish}that your son may not live much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们该快乐过日子  好好道别\N{\rEnglish}You might want to make it a happy time, say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\rEnglish}God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心脏移植是高危险的手术\N{\rEnglish}Transplantation is a high-risk operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们可能在手术台上失去他\N{\rEnglish}You could lose your son on that table.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们也许并不想冒那个险\N{\rEnglish}You might not want to take that chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是他不做手术...\N{\rEnglish}If you, you know, if he doesn't have the surgery...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不做手术  他能活多久?\N{\rEnglish}If he doesn't have the surgery, how long would he live?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会很久\N{\rEnglish}Not long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几个月  几周\N{\rEnglish}Months, weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几天\N{\rEnglish}Days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天爷\N{\rEnglish}God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别哭  宝贝  不会有事的\N{\rEnglish}Come on, baby. All right, all right, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别哭了\N{\rEnglish}Come on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉...\N{\rEnglish}I'm sorry, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太沉重了\N{\rEnglish}It's a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会陪着你的\N{\rEnglish}I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\rEnglish}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他若是你儿子  你会怎么做?\N{\rEnglish}If he was your son, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会做移植手术  毫无疑问\N{\rEnglish}I'd do the transplant, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗?\N{\rEnglish}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  就做吧  做手术\N{\rEnglish}Okay, let's do that. Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的?\N{\rEnglish}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的\N{\rEnglish}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先让麦克排上等待移植名单\N{\rEnglish}First, we've got to get Mike on the organ recipient list.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他血型B型阳性  可以排第一\N{\rEnglish}He's B-positive, so he should go right to the top of the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没这么简单\N{\rEnglish}It's not so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他考量...\N{\rEnglish}There are other considerations...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.01,0:21:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在接受移植者登上名单之前\N{\rEnglish}before a prospective recipient can be placed on a donor list.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.11,0:21:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,器官移植手术很花钱\N{\rEnglish}Transplant surgery is very expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大多都是贵的吓人\N{\rEnglish}In most cases, prohibitively so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有保险\N{\rEnglish}We've got insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:21:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有重大疾病保险  他有纳保\N{\rEnglish}I mean, I got major medical. He's covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们跟你的保险公司查过\N{\rEnglish}We've checked with your carrier, Mr. Archibald.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的保险不包括这种大手术\N{\rEnglish}There are no provisions in your policy for a procedure of this magnitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.93,0:22:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  不你弄错了\N{\rEnglish}Oh, no, no, no, no. That's a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说你错了\N{\rEnglish}Not that you're making the mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.53,0:22:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说我的确有保险\N{\rEnglish}I'm just saying that I'm insured.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.63,0:22:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我儿子有保险\N{\rEnglish}My son's covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.44,0:22:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢  亚契太太?\N{\rEnglish}How about you, Mrs. Archibald.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有保险吗?\N{\rEnglish}Do you have coverage?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我才刚上班几个月...\N{\rEnglish}No, I've only been at the supermarket a few months, and you don't get benefits...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.78,0:22:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不重要  我们有保险\N{\rEnglish}Doesn't matter, we got insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.78,0:22:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我知道你没有房产\N{\rEnglish}Okay, I can see here that you don't own your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有股票  债劵或投资\N{\rEnglish}You've no stocks, no bonds, no investments.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.79,0:22:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们有大约一千元的存款\N{\rEnglish}You have a little over $1000 in savings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们有保险\N{\rEnglish}But we got insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那很好  亚契先生\N{\rEnglish}That may be, very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.26,0:22:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去跟你的保险公司查清楚\N{\rEnglish}Archibald, you'll have to check withy your carrier on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.43,0:22:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时  我们只收现金\N{\rEnglish}In the meantime, we'll have to treat this as a cash account.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.70,0:22:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\rEnglish}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.97,0:22:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,器官移植要多少钱?\N{\rEnglish}How much does a transplant cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.10,0:22:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  让我...\N{\rEnglish}Wait a minute, baby, let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要多少钱?\N{\rEnglish}How much does it cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.67,0:22:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,移植手术  医师费\N{\rEnglish}Transplant surgery, doctors' fees,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.41,0:22:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,术后疗养费...抗排斥药...\N{\rEnglish}postoperative care...immunosuppressant drugs...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.14,0:22:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少需要二十五万\N{\rEnglish}you're looking at a minimum of $250,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.51,0:22:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若你们选择器官移植手术\N{\rEnglish}If you opt for transplant surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.72,0:22:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就要这么多\N{\rEnglish}that is your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.95,0:23:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但医院对于必须付现的病患\N{\rEnglish}But the hospital maintains a very strict
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有严格的规定\N{\rEnglish}policy with regard to cash patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在把病患名列等待移植名单前\N{\rEnglish}We require a down payment before
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.19,0:23:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要求先付头款\N{\rEnglish}we put a patient's name on a receiver's list.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.23,0:23:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是多少?\N{\rEnglish}How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的头款?\N{\rEnglish}What kind of down payment?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.09,0:23:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三成\N{\rEnglish}Thirty percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.46,0:23:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七万五千元\N{\rEnglish}Seventy-five thousand dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七万五千元...\N{\rEnglish}Seventy-five thousand dollars...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就为了把我儿子的名字放上去\N{\rEnglish}to put my son's name on a list.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.70,0:23:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我儿子病危  你却满嘴铜臭\N{\rEnglish}Our son is dying and all you can do is talk about money?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.91,0:23:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医疗是有成本的\N{\rEnglish}It costs money to provide health care.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.04,0:23:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们花钱  我们也要花钱\N{\rEnglish}It's expensive for you, it's expensive for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.68,0:23:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉\N{\rEnglish}Now, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.51,0:23:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们得保证在安排名单前付款\N{\rEnglish}You'll have to guarantee payment before I can put your son's name on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.29,0:23:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚契先生  太太  请等一下\N{\rEnglish}Mr. And Mrs. Archibald? Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.99,0:23:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你们不医  可以\N{\rEnglish}If you people won't treat us, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.73,0:23:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们带他去公立医院\N{\rEnglish}We'll take him to County Memorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我  别那么做\N{\rEnglish}You don't want to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.43,0:23:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公立医院必须救治他\N{\rEnglish}It's a county hospital. They have to treat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.13,0:23:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不行\N{\rEnglish}No, they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.23,0:23:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心脏移植是选择性手术\N{\rEnglish}Heart transplantation is considered an elective procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.47,0:23:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我  来这里绝对没错\N{\rEnglish}Believe me, you're in the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.67,0:23:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们该怎么办?\N{\rEnglish}What are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.07,0:23:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再去跟你们的保险公司谈谈\N{\rEnglish}You talk to your insurance company again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.84,0:24:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找我们人力资源部请求资助\N{\rEnglish}Check with our Human Resources office for medical assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.68,0:24:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们有钱\N{\rEnglish}There's money.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.51,0:24:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去儿童福利局  申请医疗补助\N{\rEnglish}There's Children Stats Services and there's Medicaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.11,0:24:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找办法让他留在这里\N{\rEnglish}You find a way to keep him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.62,0:24:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要接受任何人的拒绝\N{\rEnglish}You don't take no for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.75,0:24:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的保单变更过了  亚契先生\N{\rEnglish}Your policy has changed, Mr. Archibald.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.49,0:24:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变更什么?\N{\rEnglish}Changed to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.13,0:24:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们最近更换了承保组织  从PPO改为HMO\N{\rEnglish}We've recently switched carriers from a PPO to an HMO.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.30,0:24:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那比较便宜\N{\rEnglish}It's less expensive
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.70,0:24:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但很不幸地  他们的限制较多\N{\rEnglish}but unfortunately there are some restrictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.77,0:24:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么限制?\N{\rEnglish}What kind of restrictions?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.14,0:24:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情况是这样的\N{\rEnglish}Here's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.97,0:24:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非管理阶层  兼职员工  像你...\N{\rEnglish}Non-management, part-time employees, such as yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.04,0:24:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能得到第二级的巨灾保障\N{\rEnglish}only qualify for second-tier catastrophic coverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.71,0:24:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是全职  不是兼职\N{\rEnglish}No, I'm not part-time, I'm full-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.18,0:24:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是工厂生意不好\N{\rEnglish}It's just slow now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.18,0:24:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rEnglish}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.02,0:24:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你的保险以工时为计算基础...\N{\rEnglish}But your coverage is based on hours worked...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.82,0:24:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过  你只能得到第二级保障...\N{\rEnglish}and like I said, you only qualify for second tier...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.42,0:24:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保险给付最高是二万元\N{\rEnglish}and that has a maximum payout limit of $20,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.39,0:24:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\rEnglish}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.30,0:24:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公司每周按时扣我的款\N{\rEnglish}You take money out of my check every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.67,0:24:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我付保险费已经付好几年了...\N{\rEnglish}I've been paying into this policy for years...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.67,0:24:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rEnglish}Right,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.53,0:25:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们会全额给付二万元\N{\rEnglish}and that's why we'll cover you for the full 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.04,0:25:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你骗我  对吧?\N{\rEnglish}You're kidding me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.74,0:25:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说你改变了我的承保条件\N{\rEnglish}I mean, come on. You're telling me that you've dropped me from full-time to part-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.85,0:25:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们换了承保组织\N{\rEnglish}You switched carriers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.32,0:25:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却告诉我  我保障不够?\N{\rEnglish}Now you're telling me that I'm not fully covered?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.78,0:25:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我手上保单说我有保障?\N{\rEnglish}Even though I got a policy that says I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.16,0:25:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这似乎不太对  对吧?\N{\rEnglish}It doesn't seem right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.26,0:25:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rEnglish}No, it doesn't seem right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.36,0:25:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我儿子命在旦夕\N{\rEnglish}My son is very sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.13,0:25:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我没保险  问题就大了\N{\rEnglish}If I'm not covered, I got a serious problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.09,0:25:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  但我无能为力\N{\rEnglish}I understand that. But there's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.70,0:25:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着  你可以上诉\N{\rEnglish}You can file an appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.70,0:25:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?\N{\rEnglish}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.80,0:25:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去\N{\rEnglish}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.27,0:25:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要费时约七个工作天\N{\rEnglish}That takes about seven working days.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.64,0:25:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"约翰Q(父亲)"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.94,0:25:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"总薪金(税前)$18200"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.12,0:25:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面写你们已经有医疗保险了\N{\rEnglish}Says here you already have medical insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.56,0:25:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不够\N{\rEnglish}Not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.32,0:25:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们仅有的保险给付已经用尽\N{\rEnglish}What little we have is already used up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.06,0:25:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有接受政府救济吗?\N{\rEnglish}You on welfare?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.16,0:25:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\rEnglish}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.76,0:26:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们应该接受的\N{\rEnglish}You should be on welfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.30,0:26:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救济?  我们都有工作啊\N{\rEnglish}Welfare? We both have jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.17,0:26:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太糟了\N{\rEnglish}That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.10,0:26:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我帮不上忙\N{\rEnglish}I'm sorry, I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.30,0:26:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去找郡政府要医疗补助吧\N{\rEnglish}Try County Medical.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.27,0:26:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要找承办财务补助的人员\N{\rEnglish}I need to speak to somebody in financial aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.51,0:26:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想等\N{\rEnglish}I don't want to hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.08,0:26:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已等15分钟了  我不要等\N{\rEnglish}I've been holding for 15 minutes. I don't want to hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.19,0:26:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有吼\N{\rEnglish}I'm not yelling!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.42,0:26:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有  你在里面吼\N{\rEnglish}Yes, you yelling in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.93,0:26:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一位\N{\rEnglish}Next, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.10,0:26:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,排错了  15号窗口\N{\rEnglish}Wrong line. Number 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.44,0:26:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\rEnglish}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.71,0:26:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,15号窗口...\N{\rEnglish}Window 15...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.63,0:27:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\rEnglish}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.66,0:27:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行什么?\N{\rEnglish}No, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.43,0:27:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  你资格不符\N{\rEnglish}No, you don't qualify.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.66,0:27:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我儿子病危  我破产\N{\rEnglish}My son's dying, I'm broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.30,0:27:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我不够资格  谁够?\N{\rEnglish}If I don't quality, who does?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.60,0:27:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉\N{\rEnglish}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.40,0:27:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你抱歉?\N{\rEnglish}You're sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.10,0:27:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要你抱歉  我要你帮我\N{\rEnglish}I don't need you to be sorry. I need you to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.95,0:27:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"奈曼机械"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.82,0:27:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"您的上诉申请已获准"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.40,0:27:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对  这是上诉\N{\rEnglish}No, no, no, this is an appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.13,0:27:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上诉是针对已申请的理赔案件\N{\rEnglish}An appeal is for an already existing claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.64,0:27:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要提出的是申诉\N{\rEnglish}You needed to file a grievance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.70,0:27:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你弄错了\N{\rEnglish}You filed the wrong paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.04,0:27:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得重提申诉  这得耗30天\N{\rEnglish}Wait...You'll have to resubmit. It could take 30 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.71,0:27:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有30天可耗\N{\rEnglish}I don't have 30 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.88,0:27:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\rEnglish}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.71,0:27:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听够藉口了\N{\rEnglish}I'm sick of the runaround.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.48,0:27:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要让我儿子排上那个名单\N{\rEnglish}What I need is my son's name on that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.48,0:28:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们尚欠三万元医药费\N{\rEnglish}Your account is in excess of $30,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.05,0:28:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医院已经尽量通融你们了\N{\rEnglish}The hospital has bent over backwards to help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.59,0:28:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?\N{\rEnglish}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.32,0:28:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rEnglish}Yes, it is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.26,0:28:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们的慷慨是有限度的\N{\rEnglish}But, there's a limit to our generosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.69,0:28:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之  你的保险没用\N{\rEnglish}Once and for all, your insurance does not cover this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.12,0:28:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧\N{\rEnglish}Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.52,0:28:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心\N{\rEnglish}Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.12,0:28:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这玩意真重\N{\rEnglish}This thing is frigging heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.12,0:28:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别挡路\N{\rEnglish}Get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.14,0:29:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"你不能说你不要投球"\N{\rEnglish}"You can't say that you're not going to pitch."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.12,0:29:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了\N{\rEnglish}Hey. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.99,0:29:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们祈祷吧\N{\rEnglish}Let us pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.23,0:29:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慈爱的天父派遣其子耶稣...\N{\rEnglish}God of mercy into whose hands your son, Jesus Christ...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.63,0:29:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在死前交付了他的灵魂\N{\rEnglish}commended his spirit at his last hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.63,0:29:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在它手中\N{\rEnglish}Into those same hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.20,0:29:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们颂扬您的仆人蒂凡尼\N{\rEnglish}we commend your servant Tiffany.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.34,0:30:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该去找那个记者\N{\rEnglish}You should try that news guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.14,0:30:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他专做特别报导的\N{\rEnglish}does all the special investigative reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.64,0:30:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个头发超整齐的家伙\N{\rEnglish}The guy with the frigging hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.14,0:30:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自恋狂  他叫什么来着?\N{\rEnglish}Pretty boy, what's his frigging name?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.11,0:30:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姓蓝\N{\rEnglish}Lampley.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.78,0:30:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓝塔克\N{\rEnglish}Tuck Lampley.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.12,0:30:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20元买电视\N{\rEnglish}Give you $20 for the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.05,0:30:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是彩色电视耶\N{\rEnglish}It's a color TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.05,0:30:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20元\N{\rEnglish}Twenty dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.16,0:30:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就找他吧  吉米\N{\rEnglish}Call him up, Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.29,0:30:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,边走边谈  我很忙  快\N{\rEnglish}Mind if we walk and talk, I'm up to here today. Go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.46,0:30:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系\N{\rEnglish}Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.53,0:30:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能帮上什么忙?\N{\rEnglish}So, what can I do you for?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.13,0:30:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我儿子麦克\N{\rEnglish}My son, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.20,0:30:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他打棒球时心脏病发\N{\rEnglish}He fell into heart failure at his little league game.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.40,0:30:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我公司本来有给我全额保险\N{\rEnglish}No I got full insurance from the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.01,0:30:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他们现在却说不能付钱\N{\rEnglish}Now, they're telling me they won't pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.64,0:30:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医院呢?  他们不能帮忙吗?\N{\rEnglish}What about the hospital? Don't they have to cover it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.28,0:30:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  他们还叫我要付现\N{\rEnglish}No, they're telling me I got to pay cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.25,0:30:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然我就得眼睁睁看儿子死\N{\rEnglish}Otherwise, I got to take my son home and watch him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.98,0:30:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天爷\N{\rEnglish}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.75,0:30:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\rEnglish}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.45,0:30:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们想也许你能做个特别报导\N{\rEnglish}We were thinking you could do one of those special-interest pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.19,0:30:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼吁捐款  写信给国会议员...\N{\rEnglish}Send donations, write your congressman...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.52,0:30:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能帮忙  任何忙都行\N{\rEnglish}Anything you can do, Mr. Lampley, would help. Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.19,0:30:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你儿子的事太惨了  我想帮忙\N{\rEnglish}What's happening to your son is outrageous and I want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.96,0:31:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我得照规矩来\N{\rEnglish}I got to run this by my producers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.53,0:31:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟大家一样都有老板\N{\rEnglish}I got bosses like everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.13,0:31:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错  没错\N{\rEnglish}Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.37,0:31:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留个电话给凯伦  就在前面\N{\rEnglish}Leave your number with Karen, up front?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.34,0:31:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  谢谢你\N{\rEnglish}Okay. Thank you very much. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.75,0:31:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出给我一百  一百吧\N{\rEnglish}Give me $100. Give me 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.62,0:31:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  那是钻戒耶\N{\rEnglish}Come on, it's a diamond ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.99,0:31:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  90  给我90\N{\rEnglish}All right, $90. Give me 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.25,0:31:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（出售）
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.37,0:32:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂?\N{\rEnglish}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.54,0:32:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他快死了\N{\rEnglish}He's going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.47,0:32:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\rEnglish}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.74,0:32:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要叫他出院\N{\rEnglish}They're releasing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.84,0:32:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁?\N{\rEnglish}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.01,0:32:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透纳医师刚离开...\N{\rEnglish}Dr. Turner just left here...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.45,0:32:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们今早请麦克出院\N{\rEnglish}and they are releasing Mike this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.65,0:32:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  他们不会送他回家的\N{\rEnglish}Baby, wait a minute. No, they won't send him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.55,0:32:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天才交钱给他们\N{\rEnglish}I gave them money yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.85,0:32:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不重要  约翰  听我说\N{\rEnglish}It doesn't matter, John, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.86,0:32:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要他出院\N{\rEnglish}They are releasing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.82,0:32:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  我跟医院谈过\N{\rEnglish}Come on, baby, I talked to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.66,0:32:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会处理的\N{\rEnglish}I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.76,0:32:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你老是说你会处理一切\N{\rEnglish}You always take care of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.70,0:32:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会的\N{\rEnglish}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.50,0:32:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但老是处理不好  对吧?\N{\rEnglish}But, it's never enough, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.07,0:32:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得想想办法\N{\rEnglish}Now, you need to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.13,0:32:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会处理的\N{\rEnglish}I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.40,0:32:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听清楚了? 想办法\N{\rEnglish}Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.98,0:33:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你复原的很好\N{\rEnglish}You're doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.05,0:33:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的  你大概重了五磅吧?\N{\rEnglish}You really are. You've gained, what, about five pounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.12,0:33:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你是这里唯一吃得下的人\N{\rEnglish}You're the only patient I have who actually eats the food in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.49,0:33:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生  请问你\N{\rEnglish}Doc, let me ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.86,0:33:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我何时才能打网球?\N{\rEnglish}How long before I'm able to play tennis?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.86,0:33:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了  干嘛急着打球?\N{\rEnglish}You couldn't play tennis before your new heart. Why would you want to play now?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.93,0:33:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改打中国结吧?\N{\rEnglish}Take up knitting, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.77,0:33:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会打网球\N{\rEnglish}I play tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.77,0:33:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不在乎  甜心\N{\rEnglish}We don't care, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.03,0:33:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去做事吧  谢谢你\N{\rEnglish}Please get back to work. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.57,0:33:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海蒂  安排我们下周共进晚餐\N{\rEnglish}Heidi, make an appointment for us to have dinner next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.04,0:33:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来做菜\N{\rEnglish}I'm going to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.57,0:33:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  千万不要\N{\rEnglish}No, you're not going to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.01,0:34:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可别穿性感内衣绕着他转\N{\rEnglish}And you're not wearing any lingerie around him for the next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.81,0:34:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他遗产没你的份  他告诉我的\N{\rEnglish}Because you're not in his will, he told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.81,0:34:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别冒不必要的风险\N{\rEnglish}So, don't push your luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.25,0:34:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天交了六千元给医院\N{\rEnglish}I gave the hospital $6000 yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.29,0:34:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能跟你谈谈吗?\N{\rEnglish}Can I talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.69,0:34:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  没问题\N{\rEnglish}Yes, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.89,0:34:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.29,0:34:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好照顾他\N{\rEnglish}Okay, take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.86,0:34:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\rEnglish}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.64,0:34:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太太说你要麦克出院  是吗?\N{\rEnglish}My wife says you're sending Michael home. Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.67,0:34:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚契先生  我只是医生\N{\rEnglish}Mr. Archibald, I'm a physician.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.01,0:34:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政策不是我决定的\N{\rEnglish}I don't make policy decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.68,0:34:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是由董事会决定\N{\rEnglish}That's handled by the board of trustees.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.35,0:34:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是心脏外科主任\N{\rEnglish}You're the head of Cardiac Surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.98,0:34:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你建议  他们会听\N{\rEnglish}You make a recommendation, they'll listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.38,0:34:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我常常作建议\N{\rEnglish}I make recommendations all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.05,0:34:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但最后决定权在董事会 就这样  把他送回家\N{\rEnglish}The final decision rests with the board, not me. That's it. Send him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.06,0:34:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的\N{\rEnglish}I'm afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.83,0:34:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能一起散个步吗?\N{\rEnglish}Can we take a little walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.80,0:34:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会太久  我保证\N{\rEnglish}It won't take long, I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.10,0:34:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.17,0:35:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我昨晚看医院简介\N{\rEnglish}So, I'm looking at the brochure last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.67,0:35:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面写说 每年做超过三百件心脏手术\N{\rEnglish}It says that this hospital does over 300 heart surgeries a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.87,0:35:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三百件手术\N{\rEnglish}Three-hundred surgeries.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.44,0:35:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每件收25万  共有多少呢?\N{\rEnglish}Two-hundred fifty thousand dollars a pop. You know how much that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.04,0:35:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我算过了\N{\rEnglish}I did the math.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.38,0:35:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心脏手术就值七千五百万...\N{\rEnglish}That's 75 million dollars worth of heart surgeries...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.25,0:35:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你却不能帮我的忙  一个忙都不帮\N{\rEnglish}and you can't do one for me in good faith?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.45,0:35:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰  我没收你儿子诊疗费\N{\rEnglish}John, I waived my fee in your son's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.35,0:35:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是要你免费\N{\rEnglish}I'm not asking you to waive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.89,0:35:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人要你免费看病\N{\rEnglish}Nobody asked you to waive the fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.32,0:35:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能筹到钱\N{\rEnglish}I can raise the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.46,0:35:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已筹到两万二  我付钱了\N{\rEnglish}I already came up with $22,000. I paid you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.06,0:35:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向上帝发誓  我会付钱\N{\rEnglish}I swear to God on my life, I'll pay for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.33,0:35:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要给我个机会\N{\rEnglish}Just give me the opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.80,0:35:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我工时已被减成20小时了\N{\rEnglish}I'm only getting 20 hours on the job. You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.37,0:35:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做得到  我能付钱  我发誓\N{\rEnglish}I can do this. I can pay, I swear to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.07,0:35:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会付钱的\N{\rEnglish}I'll pay you the money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.74,0:35:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知怎么付  但我发誓会付\N{\rEnglish}I don't know how, but I promise I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.04,0:35:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要相信我\N{\rEnglish}You just got to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.24,0:35:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向你发誓  拜托\N{\rEnglish}I give you my word as a man. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.52,0:35:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你把手拿开好吗?\N{\rEnglish}Could you take your hands off me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.15,0:35:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经尽力了  抱歉\N{\rEnglish}I've done everything I can, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.89,0:35:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有\N{\rEnglish}No, you haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.96,0:35:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有\N{\rEnglish}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.09,0:35:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们进去谈吧\N{\rEnglish}Let's go inside and talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.50,0:36:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不再求人了  我告诉你\N{\rEnglish}I'm not asking anymore, doctor. I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.00,0:36:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我儿子弄颗新心脏  懂吗?\N{\rEnglish}You are going to give my son a new heart, you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.07,0:36:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  我明白\N{\rEnglish}Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.01,0:36:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.41,0:36:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.15,0:36:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别动\N{\rEnglish}Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.18,0:36:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准动\N{\rEnglish}Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.63,0:36:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想都别想\N{\rEnglish}Don't even think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.46,0:36:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手放下\N{\rEnglish}Put your hands down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.20,0:36:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚契先生...\N{\rEnglish}Mr. Archibald...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.27,0:36:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴\N{\rEnglish}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.00,0:36:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你不爽  但不能这样\N{\rEnglish}I know you're upset. But this is not the way to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.44,0:36:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不能走这边\N{\rEnglish}Hey, you can't go through this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.64,0:36:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手举起来\N{\rEnglish}Put your hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.14,0:36:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,举起来  举起来\N{\rEnglish}Put them up! Put them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.08,0:36:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把枪给我\N{\rEnglish}Give me your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.18,0:36:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有枪\N{\rEnglish}I don't have a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.01,0:36:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们没枪  他们没武装\N{\rEnglish}They don't have guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.65,0:36:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  好吧\N{\rEnglish}All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.18,0:36:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手放下  坐下\N{\rEnglish}put your hands down, sit down, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.65,0:36:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  站起来\N{\rEnglish}No, no, get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.75,0:37:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这会给你儿子带来危险的\N{\rEnglish}You fail to realize the jeopardy that you are putting your son in.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.49,0:37:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得谈谈...\N{\rEnglish}We've got to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.29,0:37:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴  别动\N{\rEnglish}Shut up. Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.59,0:37:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  快住手\N{\rEnglish}Okay, just stop, stop, stop, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.96,0:37:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  快住手  你若再继续...\N{\rEnglish}Okay, just stop, because if you do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.67,0:37:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就走上不归路了  你懂吗?\N{\rEnglish}you're in an irreversible course of action. You understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.80,0:37:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,踩个刹车想清楚\N{\rEnglish}Put on the brakes and think about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.80,0:37:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得谈谈\N{\rEnglish}We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.31,0:37:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚契先生  我希望...\N{\rEnglish}Mr. Archibald, I hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.51,0:37:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你退后\N{\rEnglish}Back up, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.61,0:37:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\rEnglish}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.41,0:37:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照他说的去做\N{\rEnglish}Do as he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.24,0:37:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你退后\N{\rEnglish}Please back up?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.21,0:37:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛?\N{\rEnglish}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.18,0:37:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接纳了你的建议\N{\rEnglish}Taking your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.98,0:37:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不再接受任何人的拒绝了\N{\rEnglish}I'm not taking no for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.85,0:37:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人有枪\N{\rEnglish}That guy's got a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.83,0:37:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛?  你在干嘛?\N{\rEnglish}What are you doing? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.29,0:37:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退回去  别管闲事\N{\rEnglish}Get back over there! Sit on your hands over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.23,0:37:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去\N{\rEnglish}Get over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.47,0:37:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透纳  每个人  坐下\N{\rEnglish}Turner, everybody! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.97,0:37:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透纳  坐下\N{\rEnglish}Turner, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.17,0:37:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在自己的手上\N{\rEnglish}Sit on your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.90,0:37:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的手放在屁股下\N{\rEnglish}Put your hands under your butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.11,0:37:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都别动\N{\rEnglish}Don't anybody move!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.18,0:37:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛?\N{\rEnglish}Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.25,0:38:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在流血  我是来缝合手指的\N{\rEnglish}I'm bleeding. Trying to get my goddamn fingers sewn back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.05,0:38:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚契先生  这些人是无辜的\N{\rEnglish}Mr. Archibald, these people have nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.19,0:38:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得放他们走  他们需要就医\N{\rEnglish}Let them go. They need treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.06,0:38:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是医生干嘛不动手? 医他吧\N{\rEnglish}This is hospital. You're doctor. Why don't you treat them? Start with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.76,0:38:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  医生?\N{\rEnglish}What's the matter, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.50,0:38:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要先检查他的保险卡吗?\N{\rEnglish}You want to see his insurance card first?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.90,0:38:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来\N{\rEnglish}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.44,0:38:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  你来\N{\rEnglish}Okay, you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.07,0:38:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我老婆要生孩子了\N{\rEnglish}I got a pregnant wife, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.87,0:38:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  好  好\N{\rEnglish}Okay, all right. All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.88,0:38:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着  等等  大家听着\N{\rEnglish}Listen, wait. Listen, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.62,0:38:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  这间医院换新老板了\N{\rEnglish}All right, the hospital's under new management now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.09,0:38:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rEnglish}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.95,0:38:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起大家看病免费  怎样?\N{\rEnglish}From now on, free health care for everybody. How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.16,0:38:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶  老兄\N{\rEnglish}Oh, righteous, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.46,0:38:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别一直用力压啊\N{\rEnglish}Don't squeeze it like you crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.83,0:38:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字?\N{\rEnglish}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.06,0:38:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦斯\N{\rEnglish}Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.66,0:38:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦斯  你跟透纳医生  跟我来\N{\rEnglish}Max, you and Dr. Turner, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.63,0:38:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有那台电梯的钥匙吗?\N{\rEnglish}You got keys for that elevator?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.94,0:38:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  我要你关闭电源\N{\rEnglish}Okay. I want you to kill the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.13,0:39:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意看着他  麦斯\N{\rEnglish}Keep an eye on him, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.60,0:39:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别乱动  这样我没法子缝\N{\rEnglish}Sit still. I can't do this if you're moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.83,0:39:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是青年才俊\N{\rEnglish}You remind me of Doogie Howser.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.07,0:39:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们比那个黑鬼早到的\N{\rEnglish}Hey, we were here before the black guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.50,0:39:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都会轮的到\N{\rEnglish}Everybody will get their turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.84,0:39:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们暂时会留在这里  忍着点\N{\rEnglish}We're not going anywhere for a while, so sit tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.77,0:39:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着  放轻松点  好吗?\N{\rEnglish}Look, just relax, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.39,0:39:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂?\N{\rEnglish}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.62,0:39:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂?\N{\rEnglish}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.42,0:39:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  是希望纪念医院吗?\N{\rEnglish}Hello, is this Hope Memorial Hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.66,0:39:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对  这是希望纪念医院急诊室\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, this is Hope Memorial, Emergency Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.63,0:39:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问该怎么走才能到医院\N{\rEnglish}Could you give me directions? I need to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.46,0:39:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\rEnglish}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.23,0:39:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\rEnglish}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.96,0:39:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  太太\N{\rEnglish}No, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.63,0:40:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们闭馆维修  你得打...\N{\rEnglish}We're closed for repairs. You'll have to call...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.70,0:40:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思?  这很紧急的\N{\rEnglish}What do you mean? This is an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.20,0:40:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这很紧急\N{\rEnglish}I understand that it's an emergency, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.54,0:40:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你试过天使医院吗?\N{\rEnglish}Have you tried Mount Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.44,0:40:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道那里怎么去?\N{\rEnglish}I don't know how to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.28,0:40:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平常都是我老公开车\N{\rEnglish}My husband usually drives.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.48,0:40:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要人告诉我怎么走\N{\rEnglish}I'm going to need some directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.48,0:40:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪里来的?\N{\rEnglish}Which way are you coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.72,0:40:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  往佛洛街开去  右转\N{\rEnglish}Ok, Go down Flower, make a right turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.09,0:40:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直走到底左转  懂了吗?\N{\rEnglish}Go to the end, make a left. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.56,0:40:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我怎么办?\N{\rEnglish}What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.22,0:40:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  出来\N{\rEnglish}Miss, get out from under there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.23,0:40:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我在哪生小孩?\N{\rEnglish}Where do you want me to have this baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.23,0:40:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出来  快出来\N{\rEnglish}Come from out of there. Come on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.40,0:40:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去坐在那边\N{\rEnglish}Go sit over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.57,0:40:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思议  这地方真可笑\N{\rEnglish}Unbelievable. This place is a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.81,0:40:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好我没受伤\N{\rEnglish}Good thing I'm not cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.04,0:40:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然我就死定了  对吧?\N{\rEnglish}I'd bleed to death in this joint. Right, my man?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.01,0:40:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  老兄\N{\rEnglish}Excuse me, brother man.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.51,0:40:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  你得采取行动  好吗?\N{\rEnglish}No, no, no. You need to do something, Steve, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.58,0:40:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得起来  做点什么\N{\rEnglish}You need to get your butt up, and you need to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.92,0:40:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,采取行动\N{\rEnglish}Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.42,0:40:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蜜丽  坐下\N{\rEnglish}Miriam, please sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.36,0:40:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要坐\N{\rEnglish}No, I don't want to sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.42,0:40:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么了?\N{\rEnglish}What is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.89,0:40:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等等\N{\rEnglish}Wait a minute. Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.66,0:41:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别激动  孩子还没生呢\N{\rEnglish}Relax. Don't have the baby yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.26,0:41:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何时会生?\N{\rEnglish}What is it due?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.90,0:41:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随时\N{\rEnglish}Any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.70,0:41:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  还没生\N{\rEnglish}Okay, all right. Don't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.47,0:41:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要生了\N{\rEnglish}I'm having it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.43,0:41:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没  撑着点\N{\rEnglish}Not yet. Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.67,0:41:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老兄\N{\rEnglish}Hey, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.64,0:41:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她要生了  等一下\N{\rEnglish}She's having a baby. Hang on for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.54,0:41:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  老兄\N{\rEnglish}Excuse me, brother man.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.64,0:41:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下  这位女士要生了\N{\rEnglish}Can you hang on?! The woman's having a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.74,0:41:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她何时能看医生?\N{\rEnglish}When is she going to see a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.01,0:41:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下\N{\rEnglish}Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.28,0:41:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下\N{\rEnglish}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.18,0:41:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\rEnglish}That 's cool, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.01,0:41:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莱医生\N{\rEnglish}Dr. Klein!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.22,0:41:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上过去\N{\rEnglish}I'll be there in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.72,0:41:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我没过节  你懂吧?\N{\rEnglish}You and me, we got no problems. You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.75,0:41:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我们没过节  坐好\N{\rEnglish}That's right, we don't have a problem. Just staying in the seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.19,0:41:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听不懂你在说什么\N{\rEnglish}I don't understand what you're saying, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.03,0:41:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵?  耳朵感染?\N{\rEnglish}The ear? Ear infection?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.47,0:41:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能帮她医治吗?\N{\rEnglish}Can you help her?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.97,0:41:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我?\N{\rEnglish}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.77,0:41:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你\N{\rEnglish}You.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.67,0:41:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\rEnglish}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.67,0:41:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?\N{\rEnglish}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.94,0:41:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不懂  我第一天上班\N{\rEnglish}I don't know anything. It's my first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.99,0:41:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都到另一个房间去\N{\rEnglish}Everybody in the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.29,0:42:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家现在就去另一个房间\N{\rEnglish}Everybody in the other room right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.09,0:42:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会医好你  我保证\N{\rEnglish}We'll take great care of you. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.76,0:42:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持清醒\N{\rEnglish}Stay focused on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.26,0:42:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门\N{\rEnglish}Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.93,0:42:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门  有枪伤病患\N{\rEnglish}Open up. We got a gunshot victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.63,0:42:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他大量失血\N{\rEnglish}He's lost a lot of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.87,0:42:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去别家医院\N{\rEnglish}Go to another hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.14,0:42:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快开门\N{\rEnglish}Let's go. Open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.07,0:42:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认得这些人?\N{\rEnglish}You now these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.98,0:42:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,认得\N{\rEnglish}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.28,0:42:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你确定?\N{\rEnglish}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.28,0:42:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们常来这里\N{\rEnglish}They're here all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.81,0:42:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门\N{\rEnglish}Open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.55,0:42:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的外套脱掉\N{\rEnglish}Take your jacket off.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.55,0:42:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\rEnglish}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.89,0:42:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点  快脱掉\N{\rEnglish}Open it up. Take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.26,0:42:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它放地上  走开  把他留下\N{\rEnglish}Just put it on the ground. Walk away. Leave him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.13,0:42:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下他就对了  快走\N{\rEnglish}Just leave. Go, go. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.46,0:42:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\rEnglish}Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.67,0:42:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么了?\N{\rEnglish}What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.54,0:42:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他中枪了\N{\rEnglish}He got shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.98,0:42:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  走吧\N{\rEnglish}All right, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.02,0:43:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  这袋子里是什么\N{\rEnglish}Hey, wait, I want to see what's in this bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.53,0:43:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了?\N{\rEnglish}What happened to you, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.43,0:43:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把收银机里的钱都给了他们\N{\rEnglish}I gave them all the money in the register.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.63,0:43:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他们还是对我开枪\N{\rEnglish}They shot me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.63,0:43:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天爷\N{\rEnglish}Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.44,0:43:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他得立刻手术  送进外伤病房\N{\rEnglish}He needs surgery now. Can I take him to Trauma one?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.87,0:43:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.54,0:43:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\rEnglish}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.11,0:43:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何?\N{\rEnglish}What do we got?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.31,0:43:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腹部枪伤\N{\rEnglish}Gunshot wound to the belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.78,0:43:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,急救人员有做任何处置吗?\N{\rEnglish}Did we get anything from the EMTs?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.98,0:43:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\rEnglish}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.65,0:43:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透纳医生  我们需要你帮忙\N{\rEnglish}Doc Turner, we'll need a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.28,0:43:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\rEnglish}Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.85,0:43:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我一把吧?\N{\rEnglish}Give me a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.79,0:43:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三  二  一  抬起来\N{\rEnglish}Three, two, one, lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.55,0:43:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\rEnglish}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.72,0:43:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮不上忙  这是枪伤\N{\rEnglish}No, I can't handle this. This is a gut shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.49,0:43:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是心脏外科的  不是急诊科\N{\rEnglish}I'm a cardiac surgeon. I'm not an Emergency Room physician.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.83,0:43:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这跟骑脚踏车一样简单\N{\rEnglish}It's like riding a bike, doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.00,0:43:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就假装你有收费吧\N{\rEnglish}Pretend you're getting paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.97,0:43:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是萍果跟橘子的差别  不行\N{\rEnglish}This is apples and oranges, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.03,0:43:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他快死了  救救他\N{\rEnglish}He's dying. Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.50,0:43:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想救他  但我没有...\N{\rEnglish}I'd like to help him. I haven't done...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.50,0:43:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动手吧\N{\rEnglish}Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.14,0:44:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注射止痛剂  局部麻醉\N{\rEnglish}Seventy-five milligrams Demerol I.V. Lidocaine, two percent local.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.18,0:44:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻洗手\N{\rEnglish}Scrub right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.18,0:44:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局部麻醉免了  改全身麻醉\N{\rEnglish}Forget the local. I'm putting him to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.18,0:44:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出去后要告这家医院跟保安\N{\rEnglish}When I get out of here, I'm suing this hospital and your security company.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.52,0:44:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你凭什么认为你一定能出去?\N{\rEnglish}What makes you so sure you're getting out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.76,0:44:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了\N{\rEnglish}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.41,0:44:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  请站到线后\N{\rEnglish}All right, you got to stand behind the line, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.32,0:44:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这辆车弄出去  谢谢\N{\rEnglish}Move this out of here for me? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.69,0:44:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副队长  麻烦大了\N{\rEnglish}Lieutenant. We got a real problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.39,0:44:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么麻烦?\N{\rEnglish}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.06,0:44:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙准备长期抗战\N{\rEnglish}This guy's in for the long haul.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.79,0:44:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他锁住急诊室\N{\rEnglish}He's locked the E.R.,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.19,0:44:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把自己困在里面  关闭电梯电源\N{\rEnglish}barricaded himself in and killed the power in the elevators.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.43,0:44:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们若破门而入 他会大开杀戒\N{\rEnglish}If we bust down the door, this son of a bitch might start killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.57,0:45:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,急诊室里有两架监视摄影机\N{\rEnglish}There's two video cameras hidden in the E.R.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.14,0:45:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是属于医院监视系统\N{\rEnglish}The hospital's surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.10,0:45:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在设法连结视讯\N{\rEnglish}We're setting up a video tap.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.41,0:45:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你负责保全?\N{\rEnglish}You in charge of security?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.51,0:45:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  是皮瓦利  他今天休假\N{\rEnglish}No. That's Wally Pitoniak. It's his day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.74,0:45:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不再是了  叫他过来\N{\rEnglish}Not anymore, it ain't. Get him down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.32,0:45:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能弄条安全的通话线路吗?\N{\rEnglish}Can you get me a secure line?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.62,0:45:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行\N{\rEnglish}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.12,0:45:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副队长  里面的人有无线电\N{\rEnglish}Lieutenant, we got one of our guys on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.39,0:45:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也许会想试试\N{\rEnglish}He's got a walkie-talkie. You might want to try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.32,0:45:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切断急诊室的电话线路\N{\rEnglish}Put a clamp on all pone lines to the E.R.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.79,0:45:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他若拿起电话  我要他跟我谈\N{\rEnglish}If he picks up the phone, I want him talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.39,0:45:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题\N{\rEnglish}Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.90,0:45:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁是这里的负责人?\N{\rEnglish}Who's in charge here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.93,0:45:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丽贝卡\N{\rEnglish}Rebecca Payne, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.50,0:45:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她今天也休假\N{\rEnglish}It's her day off too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.93,0:45:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天  这医院到底有没有人上班\N{\rEnglish}Does anybody work at this hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.90,0:45:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是周六\N{\rEnglish}It's Saturday, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.07,0:45:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样?\N{\rEnglish}So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.74,0:45:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,周六也会有人生病  不是吗?\N{\rEnglish}People get sick on Saturday, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.65,0:45:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没哭了\N{\rEnglish}No cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.48,0:45:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没哭了\N{\rEnglish}No cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.29,0:45:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚契先生  我要帮她做内诊\N{\rEnglish}Mr. Archibald, I need to do an internal exam on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.39,0:45:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要带她去哪?\N{\rEnglish}Where are you going to take here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.69,0:45:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边的诊疗室\N{\rEnglish}Examination room there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.03,0:45:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  去吧\N{\rEnglish}Good. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.73,0:46:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\rEnglish}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.60,0:46:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记住  这不是你的错\N{\rEnglish}Remember, it ain't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.50,0:46:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\rEnglish}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.87,0:46:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我未婚妻的手可能断了\N{\rEnglish}I think my fiancee might have broken her arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.41,0:46:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有人能医治她?\N{\rEnglish}Could somebody take a look at her, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.75,0:46:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然  怎么回事?\N{\rEnglish}Sure, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.71,0:46:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个醉鬼闯红灯...\N{\rEnglish}A drunk ran a red light...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.02,0:46:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他撞上我们\N{\rEnglish}He slammed into us.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.62,0:46:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧?\N{\rEnglish}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.18,0:46:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\rEnglish}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.25,0:46:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是个意外\N{\rEnglish}It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.25,0:46:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rEnglish}Yes, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.59,0:46:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是警察\N{\rEnglish}This is the police department.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.39,0:46:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟负责的人谈\N{\rEnglish}I'm speaking to the man in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.86,0:46:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请打开无线电\N{\rEnglish}Please pick up the walkie-talkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.66,0:46:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这栋建筑已被团团围住\N{\rEnglish}The building is surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.43,0:46:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们已无法出入\N{\rEnglish}There's no way in or out,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.67,0:46:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你若听见  我建议你接听\N{\rEnglish}So if you hear me, I advise you to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.24,0:46:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂?\N{\rEnglish}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.37,0:46:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂?  有人在吗?\N{\rEnglish}Hello? Is anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.51,0:46:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有\N{\rEnglish}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.21,0:46:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是芝加哥警局的葛副队长\N{\rEnglish}This is Lieutenant Frank Grimes of the Chicago Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.75,0:46:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是负责的人?\N{\rEnglish}Are you the man in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.88,0:46:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rEnglish}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.39,0:46:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问你是?\N{\rEnglish}Who am I speaking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.92,0:47:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰...\N{\rEnglish}John...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.89,0:47:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老Q\N{\rEnglish}Q.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.93,0:47:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  约翰老Q\N{\rEnglish}All right, John Q.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.76,0:47:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重覆  我是葛副队长\N{\rEnglish}Again, I'm Lieutenant Grimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.03,0:47:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我要你叫我法兰  可以吗?\N{\rEnglish}But I want you to call me Frank. Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.07,0:47:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  法兰\N{\rEnglish}Sure, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.44,0:47:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我负责人质谈判\N{\rEnglish}I'll be the hostage negotiator.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.07,0:47:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当警察35年  我都这么做\N{\rEnglish}I've been a cop for 35 years. This is all I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.38,0:47:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不玩花样  也不耍人\N{\rEnglish}I don't play games. I don't fool around.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.14,0:47:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说的话  你绝对可以相信\N{\rEnglish}So if I say something, you can take it to the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.61,0:47:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们来谈谈吧\N{\rEnglish}Now, let's get down to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.62,0:47:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人受伤吗?\N{\rEnglish}Is anybody hurt?
