Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.83,0:47:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么?\N{\rEnglish}What is it that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.93,0:47:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找到丽贝卡\N{\rEnglish}You find Rebecca Payne,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.20,0:47:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望纪念医院的行政主管\N{\rEnglish}Hope Memorial's administrative supervisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.43,0:47:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到她\N{\rEnglish}You find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.77,0:47:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫她把我孩子放上移植名单\N{\rEnglish}You tell her I want my kid's name on the donor's list.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.64,0:47:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听清楚了?  把我孩子放上名单\N{\rEnglish}My kid's name on the donor's list.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.64,0:47:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是儿子还是女儿?\N{\rEnglish}Kid boy or girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.64,0:47:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儿子\N{\rEnglish}A boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.94,0:47:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己有两个儿子\N{\rEnglish}I got two boys myself, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.65,0:47:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个女儿  两个儿子\N{\rEnglish}Two girls and two boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.58,0:48:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别想耍我  法兰  你明白吗?\N{\rEnglish}Don't handle me, Frank. You understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.22,0:48:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢被耍  我没那么笨\N{\rEnglish}I don't want to be handled. It insults my intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.12,0:48:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别激动  约翰  千万别激动\N{\rEnglish}Take it easy, John. The idea's not to get too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.99,0:48:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想怎样就怎样  你明白吗?\N{\rEnglish}I'm going to take it any way I can get it. You understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.26,0:48:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的要求\N{\rEnglish}Now, this is what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.50,0:48:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是做不到...\N{\rEnglish}If I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.70,0:48:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就会害死人\N{\rEnglish}there'll be some dead bodies on your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.96,0:48:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听明白了?\N{\rEnglish}Understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.73,0:48:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听的很清楚  我会写下来\N{\rEnglish}I hear you loud and clear. I'll jot that down.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.07,0:48:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丽贝卡  对吧?\N{\rEnglish}Rebecca Payne. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.04,0:48:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\rEnglish}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.87,0:48:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面有很多警察  约翰\N{\rEnglish}Now, there're a lot of cops out here, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.61,0:48:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你确定你要这么做?\N{\rEnglish}Sure you want to go through with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.51,0:48:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对  我确定\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.42,0:48:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  等着吧\N{\rEnglish}All right, sit tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.05,0:48:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的处境很艰困  有很多问题\N{\rEnglish}You're in a tough spot, John. A lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.52,0:48:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你若跟我合作  讲理一点\N{\rEnglish}But if you work with me, if you're reasonable,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.42,0:48:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们总会想出解决的办法\N{\rEnglish}we'll figure a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.42,0:48:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须对彼此有坚定信念\N{\rEnglish}We have to have faith in one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.43,0:48:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?\N{\rEnglish}Why is that, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.29,0:48:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?\N{\rEnglish}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.46,0:48:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信念就是这样\N{\rEnglish}That's what faith's all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.70,0:48:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去相信你不想相信的东西\N{\rEnglish}Believing what you don't want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.90,0:48:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样  你又能怎么办?\N{\rEnglish}Besides, what else are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.14,0:48:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要做羊膜穿刺\N{\rEnglish}I want my epidural.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.37,0:49:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了\N{\rEnglish}Too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.41,0:49:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很痛  医生...\N{\rEnglish}She's in pain, doc...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.54,0:49:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出去\N{\rEnglish}Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.71,0:49:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不会有事的\N{\rEnglish}She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.22,0:49:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一胎?\N{\rEnglish}First child?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.59,0:49:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对  没错...\N{\rEnglish}Yeah. Yeah, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.69,0:49:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有点紧张\N{\rEnglish}I'm kind of nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.60,0:49:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我以前也一样\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, I was too.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.86,0:49:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要儿子还是女儿?\N{\rEnglish}Do you want a boy or girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.33,0:49:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都好\N{\rEnglish}It doesn't matter to me, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.63,0:49:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要孩子健康就好\N{\rEnglish}As long as my kid's healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.34,0:49:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只求这样\N{\rEnglish}That's all I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.98,0:49:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着  我说这话没有恶意\N{\rEnglish}Listen, I didn't mean anything by that, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.42,0:49:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时谁在开车?\N{\rEnglish}Who was driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.49,0:49:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车子  谁在开?\N{\rEnglish}The car. Who was driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.26,0:49:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我\N{\rEnglish}I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.36,0:49:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这跟那有什么关系?\N{\rEnglish}What's that got to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.16,0:49:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她受伤  你却没有?\N{\rEnglish}Why's your girl all banged up and you're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.00,0:49:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你认为这是什么?\N{\rEnglish}What do you call this?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.64,0:50:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你笑什么?\N{\rEnglish}What are you laughing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.57,0:50:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快帮这家伙拿个OK绷吧\N{\rEnglish}Somebody get this fool a Band-Aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.04,0:50:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望你失血过多而死\N{\rEnglish}I don't want you to bleed to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.01,0:50:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去你的  这很痛的\N{\rEnglish}Screw you, man. That shit hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.68,0:50:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的安全气囊弹开  我的却没有\N{\rEnglish}His air bag went off and mine didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.98,0:50:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你开那一种车?\N{\rEnglish}What kind of car?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.02,0:50:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奔驰500\N{\rEnglish}Mercedes 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.18,0:50:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你开奔驰500?\N{\rEnglish}You drive a Mercedes 500?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.09,0:50:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪个年份的?\N{\rEnglish}What year?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.12,0:50:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1986年的\N{\rEnglish}Nineteen eighty-six.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.32,0:50:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是经典名车\N{\rEnglish}It's a classic.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.19,0:50:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奔驰的乘客座在88年以前 并没有装安全气囊\N{\rEnglish}Mercedes didn't make passenger-side air bags till 1988.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.73,0:50:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逮到了\N{\rEnglish}Busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.17,0:50:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么  约翰?\N{\rEnglish}What's your point, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.10,0:50:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢  米区?\N{\rEnglish}What's yours, Mitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.64,0:50:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重点是你竟敢痛下杀手\N{\rEnglish}Point is you from the slap-a-ho tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.77,0:50:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想甩了这位小姐\N{\rEnglish}You like to beat on the lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.61,0:50:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都明白\N{\rEnglish}and everybody here knows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.48,0:50:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时喝醉了\N{\rEnglish}I was drunk, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.69,0:50:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别在这里抽烟\N{\rEnglish}Don't smoke in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.33,0:51:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  通融一下 行个方便吧\N{\rEnglish}Come on, man. Give me a break. Work with me here.
