Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.14,0:51:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很饿  弄一桶炸鸡进来吧\N{\rEnglish}I'm hungry. Let's get a bucket of chicken in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.01,0:51:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就好  好吗?\N{\rEnglish}In a minute, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.11,0:51:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面情况如何?\N{\rEnglish}How's it going in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.28,0:51:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他死不了的\N{\rEnglish}He's going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.41,0:51:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这家伙失了多少血吗?\N{\rEnglish}Do you have any idea how much blood this guy lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.82,0:51:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思议  他救了这人一命\N{\rEnglish}It's incredible. He saved this man's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.43,0:51:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?\N{\rEnglish}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.67,0:51:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来西斯\N{\rEnglish}Lasix.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.90,0:51:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能帮他排除多馀水份的利尿剂\N{\rEnglish}It's a diuretic to help get rid of some of the fluid buildup.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.07,0:51:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他会流失钾  所以要补充这个\N{\rEnglish}But it's potassium depleting, so he needs this one to supplement.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.11,0:51:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些呢?\N{\rEnglish}And those?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.68,0:51:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度巴明是为了控制血压\N{\rEnglish}Dopamine for his blood pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.21,0:51:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛地黄刺激心脏  这是医肺积水\N{\rEnglish}Dig for his heart. Primacor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.82,0:51:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊  真多\N{\rEnglish}Gosh, it seems like so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.72,0:51:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  这是抗生素\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, it's a lot. This is antibiotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.45,0:52:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什么的?\N{\rEnglish}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.72,0:52:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是预防用药  以备万一\N{\rEnglish}Well, it's prophylactic, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.43,0:52:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些呢?\N{\rEnglish}And those?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.06,0:52:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这两个是控制疼痛的\N{\rEnglish}These two, they're for pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.83,0:52:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很不舒服\N{\rEnglish}I don't feel so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.14,0:52:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这会让你暂时觉得有点不舒服\N{\rEnglish}This'll make you feel yucky for a few minutes, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.54,0:52:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我会去拿点小冰块给你吃\N{\rEnglish}But I'm going to get you some of those crunchy ice chips to chew on.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.78,0:52:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?\N{\rEnglish}How's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.65,0:52:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了  麦克\N{\rEnglish}Hey, Mike, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.48,0:52:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚有个人过来看你\N{\rEnglish}there was this guy, he stopped by to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.02,0:52:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说他是你的朋友\N{\rEnglish}Said he was a friend of your.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.25,0:52:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把他带到这里来了\N{\rEnglish}I got him right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.55,0:52:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道该不该让他进来\N{\rEnglish}I didn't know if I should let him in or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.22,0:52:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢?\N{\rEnglish}What do you think?
