Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.36,0:52:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好\N{\rEnglish}That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.33,0:52:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.70,0:52:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\rEnglish}Thank you.
