Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.73,0:53:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸会来吧?\N{\rEnglish}Is Dad coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.70,0:53:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会  他会来\N{\rEnglish}Yeah. He's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.33,0:53:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候?  他在哪里?\N{\rEnglish}When? Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.40,0:53:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\rEnglish}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.37,0:53:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他会来的\N{\rEnglish}But he's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.65,0:53:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么?\N{\rEnglish}What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.02,0:53:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别管我  没用的家伙\N{\rEnglish}Never mind me. You're worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.22,0:53:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烂保全  你该趁机扳倒他的\N{\rEnglish}Some security guard. You should have zapped him when you had the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.42,0:53:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用什么扳倒他?\N{\rEnglish}Zap him with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.33,0:53:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何况  我才不要冒险\N{\rEnglish}Besides, I'm not sticking my neck on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.80,0:53:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又没钱可以捞\N{\rEnglish}Not for 8.50 an hour, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.34,0:54:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了?\N{\rEnglish}Are you nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.08,0:54:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在干什么?\N{\rEnglish}What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.34,0:54:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为自己找出路\N{\rEnglish}Looking out for number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.75,0:54:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想活命  就坐好等人来救\N{\rEnglish}Man, you want to stay alive, you sit tight and wait for the cavalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.95,0:54:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒吧  警方一定会杀进来\N{\rEnglish}Wake up. The cops are coming in shooting.
