Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.06,0:54:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氯乙烷  闻起来像豆蔻\N{\rEnglish}Ethyl chloride. Just like mace.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.13,0:54:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着  把那些东西放回去...\N{\rEnglish}Put the stuff back before you get us...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.10,0:54:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才给我听着  猪头警卫\N{\rEnglish}You listen to me, you stupid rent-a-cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.04,0:54:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是笨蛋\N{\rEnglish}I am not a slob.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.01,0:54:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生很棒  很重要\N{\rEnglish}I have a life, and it means something to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.48,0:54:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要死在这里  绝不\N{\rEnglish}I'm not going down in this shithole. No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.26,0:54:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  你们好\N{\rEnglish}How are you? How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.49,0:54:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  你好\N{\rEnglish}How are you? How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.06,0:54:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位好\N{\rEnglish}How are you, fellas?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.83,0:54:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暴徒是否要求让他儿子动手术?\N{\rEnglish}Is it true the man inside wants an operation for this son?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.46,0:54:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊\N{\rEnglish}Hey, how you doing, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.77,0:55:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孟局长  知道他拿什么武器吗\N{\rEnglish}Chief Monroe. Do you know what kind of weapon he has?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.57,0:55:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一知道就告诉你  好吗?\N{\rEnglish}I'll let you know when I know, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.24,0:55:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会是第一个知道的\N{\rEnglish}You'll be the first to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.97,0:55:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等下就告诉你\N{\rEnglish}I'll let you know later.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.44,0:55:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真高兴看到你  葛斯\N{\rEnglish}Good to see you, Gus.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.78,0:55:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  法兰  真受瞩目啊\N{\rEnglish}How you doing, Frank? It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.31,0:55:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.98,0:55:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?\N{\rEnglish}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.85,0:55:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太早出动大批警力了吧?\N{\rEnglish}It's early for the heavy artillery.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.68,0:55:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧  也许不会\N{\rEnglish}Maybe. Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.32,0:55:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?\N{\rEnglish}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.62,0:55:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你正目睹一切\N{\rEnglish}You're looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.05,0:55:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面有个很沮丧的父亲\N{\rEnglish}Very upset father inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.96,0:55:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得给他几分钟冷静下来\N{\rEnglish}so we're giving him a few minutes to cool off.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.73,0:55:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别给他太多时间了\N{\rEnglish}Let's not give him too much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.43,0:55:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽快解决这件事  好吗?\N{\rEnglish}Let's end this quick and quiet. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.97,0:55:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这正是我们的计划\N{\rEnglish}That's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.13,0:55:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  很好\N{\rEnglish}All right, good. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.14,0:55:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  我就在此支援吧\N{\rEnglish}In that case, I'm just here to lend my support.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.77,0:55:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要保姆  不会有问题的\N{\rEnglish}I don't need a babysitter, Gus. It's under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.04,0:55:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?\N{\rEnglish}Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.64,0:55:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rEnglish}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.21,0:55:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\rEnglish}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.48,0:55:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,街上不能有人持枪跑来跑去\N{\rEnglish}Can't have people running around the street using guns, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.81,0:55:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那会让人觉得本市很危险\N{\rEnglish}Make it look like the city's unsafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.08,0:55:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外  我必须待在这里\N{\rEnglish}Besides, I got to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.22,0:55:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让人以为局长在偷懒\N{\rEnglish}Police chief doesn't show up, looks like he's asleep at the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.72,0:55:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就别插手乱管\N{\rEnglish}Well, just stay out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.62,0:55:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电视台的摄影机在那里\N{\rEnglish}The TV cameras are over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.03,0:56:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那应该会让你觉得很自在\N{\rEnglish}Should make you feel right at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.26,0:56:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\rEnglish}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.60,0:56:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你放轻松点嘛\N{\rEnglish}Why don't you just relax?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.83,0:56:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为何老是无法放轻松?\N{\rEnglish}Why can't you relax?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.60,0:56:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很好\N{\rEnglish}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.34,0:56:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做你该做的事  我不会K你\N{\rEnglish}Do your job. I'm not here to cut your nuts off.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.60,0:56:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在做啊\N{\rEnglish}I'm doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.47,0:56:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是警察  对吧?\N{\rEnglish}We're both cops, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.61,0:56:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是站在同一边的  记得吧?\N{\rEnglish}We're on the same side, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.77,0:56:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对  对\N{\rEnglish}Right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.71,0:56:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.31,0:56:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴见到你  谢谢\N{\rEnglish}It's good to see you. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.05,0:56:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂?  是的  市长先生\N{\rEnglish}Hello? Yes, Mr. Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.68,0:56:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回头见了\N{\rEnglish}I'll see you in a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.28,0:56:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我们了解...好  我知道\N{\rEnglish}No, we got it...Okay. I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.69,0:56:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老人家在找成人纸尿布\N{\rEnglish}The old man looking for his Depends.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.96,0:56:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是不是忘在这里了?\N{\rEnglish}Did he lave them over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.10,0:56:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂为何医生们没发现\N{\rEnglish}I don't understand why they never found it, the doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.31,0:56:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我儿子出生时健康的很\N{\rEnglish}My son has had clean checkups since the day he was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.71,0:56:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生为何没发现问题?\N{\rEnglish}How could the doctors not pick it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.71,0:56:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也许并未彻底检查\N{\rEnglish}He might not have been tested thoroughly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.98,0:56:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?\N{\rEnglish}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.75,0:56:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你加入的是HMO的保险吧?\N{\rEnglish}You got an HMO, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.69,0:57:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\rEnglish}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.32,0:57:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答案就在这里\N{\rEnglish}There's your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.66,0:57:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HMO付钱请医生不要检查\N{\rEnglish}HMOs pay their doctors not to test.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.59,0:57:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样可以压低成本\N{\rEnglish}That's the way. It keeps costs down.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.46,0:57:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假设麦克需要额外的检验\N{\rEnglish}Say Mike did need additional testing,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.63,0:57:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但保险公司说他们不会付钱...\N{\rEnglish}and insurance says they won't cover it...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.93,0:57:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生就会闭上嘴...\N{\rEnglish}the doctor keeps his mouth shut...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.90,0:57:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了圣诞节\N{\rEnglish}and come Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.94,0:57:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HMO就会寄分红支票给医生\N{\rEnglish}the HMO sends the doctor a fat-ass bonus check.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.44,0:57:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?\N{\rEnglish}Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.81,0:57:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能\N{\rEnglish}Possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.51,0:57:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不一定  但有可能\N{\rEnglish}Not likely, but possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.34,0:57:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些医生可能早知道有问题...\N{\rEnglish}These doctors my have known what was wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.21,0:57:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们本可以早些治疗他的?\N{\rEnglish}and they could've treated him all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.65,0:57:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢?  我不知道  约翰\N{\rEnglish}Who knows? I don't know, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.05,0:57:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这不是攻击你  医生\N{\rEnglish}Don't take this personal, doc,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.05,0:57:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但医生真是一群骗子\N{\rEnglish}but you all a bunch of goddamn crooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.82,0:57:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别乱说话\N{\rEnglish}You don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.09,0:57:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们发的誓又是怎么回事?\N{\rEnglish}What about that thing that you guys take?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.36,0:57:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发誓?\N{\rEnglish}The thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.13,0:57:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誓言啊  你们怎么说?\N{\rEnglish}That promise. What do they call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.63,0:57:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医德伦理誓约\N{\rEnglish}The Hippocratic oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.26,0:57:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比较像是伪君子誓约吧\N{\rEnglish}More like the hypocritical oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.23,0:57:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎么说的?\N{\rEnglish}How's it go, doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.93,0:57:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我宣誓要照顾病患  尤其是濒死病患...\N{\rEnglish}"I'll solemnly swear to take care of the sick, damned near dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.44,0:57:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非他们没有保险\N{\rEnglish}unless they ain't got major medical."
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.51,0:57:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样说的吗?\N{\rEnglish}Something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.27,0:57:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的很正确  就是那样\N{\rEnglish}You got it perfectly. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.47,0:57:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这很可笑  但这离事实不远了\N{\rEnglish}Funny, but it's not far from the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.81,0:57:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事常发生\N{\rEnglish}This shit happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.51,0:57:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,急救人员送进急病伤患...\N{\rEnglish}Paramedics bring in some accident victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.65,0:58:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当会计发现他们付不出钱\N{\rEnglish}and when accounting finds out they can't pay,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.68,0:58:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就把他们送走\N{\rEnglish}they send him packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.42,0:58:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医院不能拒绝病人\N{\rEnglish}Hospitals can't turn people away.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.85,0:58:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有法律能处罚他们吗?\N{\rEnglish}Isn't there laws against that?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.95,0:58:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有  但他们有漏洞可钻\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, but there's also ways around those laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.36,0:58:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只需要先稳住他们...\N{\rEnglish}The only thing we have to do is stabilize them...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.09,0:58:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后  我们就没责任了\N{\rEnglish}and after that, we're off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.59,0:58:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情不是这样的\N{\rEnglish}That's not how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.39,0:58:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样\N{\rEnglish}That's exactly how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.23,0:58:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许心脏外科不是  但在这里...\N{\rEnglish}Maybe not on the fifth floor, but in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.87,0:58:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你没钱\N{\rEnglish}no money,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.90,0:58:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会被乱医一通  然后被踢出去\N{\rEnglish}you get a Band-Aid, a foot in the ass, and you're out the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.64,0:58:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴  够了\N{\rEnglish}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.44,0:58:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经听太多抱怨了\N{\rEnglish}I've heard all the bitching I can stand for one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.61,0:58:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们若要把我当成吸血鬼  好\N{\rEnglish}If you all want to regard me as some kind of blood-sucking vampire, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.01,0:58:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好  我就当坏蛋吧\N{\rEnglish}Great. I'll be the bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.68,0:58:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是谁拿枪在要胁人的?\N{\rEnglish}But who's holding the fucking gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.79,0:58:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官\N{\rEnglish}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.19,0:58:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副队长\N{\rEnglish}Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.63,0:58:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂?\N{\rEnglish}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.46,0:58:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\rEnglish}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.63,0:58:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰  我是葛法兰\N{\rEnglish}John, this is Frank Grimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.77,0:58:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,线路被切了\N{\rEnglish}The line is clipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.04,0:58:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿起电话就直通我这里\N{\rEnglish}You pick up the phone, you get me. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.87,0:58:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么需要我帮忙的?\N{\rEnglish}Now, what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.84,0:59:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名单的事怎么样了?\N{\rEnglish}What's going on with the list?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.94,0:59:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在设法  但我需要时间\N{\rEnglish}I'm working on it, but I need time.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.11,0:59:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没时间  法兰\N{\rEnglish}Time I don't have, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.95,0:59:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谈谈人质吧\N{\rEnglish}Let's talk about the postages.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.75,0:59:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就谈吧  你想知道什么?\N{\rEnglish}What do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.62,0:59:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面情况如何?  他们好吗?\N{\rEnglish}What's going on in there? How are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.09,0:59:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们很好\N{\rEnglish}They're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.09,0:59:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们又吃点心又讨论医疗保险\N{\rEnglish}We seating candy bars and discussing HMOs.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.29,0:59:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在等你\N{\rEnglish}We're waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.92,0:59:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放一些人出来\N{\rEnglish}Let some of them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.89,0:59:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?\N{\rEnglish}For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.89,0:59:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你忙  你也该表现诚意\N{\rEnglish}I do for you, you do for me. Show some good faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.70,0:59:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有很多人很紧张\N{\rEnglish}A lot of nervous people here, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.80,0:59:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你能放几个人  大家会轻松一点\N{\rEnglish}Make everybody breath a lot easier if we saw some happy faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.47,0:59:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你开始帮忙以后再说\N{\rEnglish}I'll do for you when you start doing for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.04,0:59:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要我儿子登上名单\N{\rEnglish}I want my kid's name on that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.61,0:59:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别耍我  法兰\N{\rEnglish}I'm not kidding around, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.88,0:59:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表现诚意  约翰\N{\rEnglish}Good faith, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.98,0:59:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诚意到此为止\N{\rEnglish}Good faith only takes you so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.71,0:59:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?  他吗?\N{\rEnglish}What's that? Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.75,0:59:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前为止你还没有帮上忙\N{\rEnglish}So far you haven't earned any points.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.35,0:59:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我要跟你谈谈\N{\rEnglish}I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.72,0:59:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.39,0:59:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她撑开了六公分  胎位不正\N{\rEnglish}She's six centimeters dilated, and the baby is breech.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.02,0:59:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得立刻把她送去产科\N{\rEnglish}We have to move her to Maternity immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.69,0:59:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰\N{\rEnglish}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.66,0:59:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  法兰\N{\rEnglish}Hang on, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.79,0:59:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里\N{\rEnglish}Right down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.46,0:59:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?\N{\rEnglish}What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.93,0:59:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,认得这个人吗?\N{\rEnglish}Do you know this man?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.27,1:00:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰·亚契  他儿子在加护病房\N{\rEnglish}His name is John Archibald. He has a son in ICU.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.14,1:00:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派人去病房  我要跟母亲谈\N{\rEnglish}Put people on the door. I need to talk to the mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.24,1:00:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在吗  法兰?\N{\rEnglish}Are you there, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.21,1:00:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在  约翰\N{\rEnglish}I'm here, John. I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.94,1:00:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我改变主意了\N{\rEnglish}I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.45,1:00:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要放一些人质\N{\rEnglish}I'll let some of the hostages go.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.08,1:00:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好  约翰  这样做很对\N{\rEnglish}That's great, John.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.68,1:00:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但等我一开始放人\N{\rEnglish}But when I do,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.82,1:00:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就开始计时了  明白吗?\N{\rEnglish}the clock starts. You understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.99,1:00:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在4点15\N{\rEnglish}It's 4:15.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.96,1:00:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有一小时  到5点15  懂吗\N{\rEnglish}You got one hour. You got till 5:15. Understand, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.09,1:00:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我儿子到时没登上名单\N{\rEnglish}If my boy's not on that list by 5:15,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.73,1:00:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就有人会丧命\N{\rEnglish}somebody is going to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.16,1:00:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰  别做傻事\N{\rEnglish}Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.26,1:00:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5点15  法兰\N{\rEnglish}5:15, Frank!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.47,1:00:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5点15分  快去设法\N{\rEnglish}Five-one-five, something happens for me!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.17,1:00:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了\N{\rEnglish}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.04,1:00:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是警察  快找验尸官吧\N{\rEnglish}You're a cop. Call the coroner.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.67,1:00:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太糟了  法兰\N{\rEnglish}This is bad, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.74,1:00:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一定要赶快解决\N{\rEnglish}This has just got to go away.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.78,1:00:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  蜜丽\N{\rEnglish}All right, Miriam.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.45,1:00:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放轻松  不会有事的\N{\rEnglish}Relax, everything's going to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.12,1:00:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的宝贝会很好的  别担心\N{\rEnglish}Our baby will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.42,1:00:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有萝莎\N{\rEnglish}And Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.95,1:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\rEnglish}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.49,1:00:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\rEnglish}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.36,1:00:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚契先生\N{\rEnglish}Mr. Archibald?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.39,1:00:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让我先生一起走\N{\rEnglish}Please let my husband come with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.06,1:01:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  你先出去  我不会有事的\N{\rEnglish}Baby, no, I need you to get out of here. I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.90,1:01:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走好了  我无牵无挂\N{\rEnglish}Shit, I'll go. I'm free.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.87,1:01:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史提  不要\N{\rEnglish}Steve, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.53,1:01:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你算不算男人啊?\N{\rEnglish}What kind of man are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.77,1:01:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去你的  黑金刚\N{\rEnglish}Screw you, Tyrone.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.37,1:01:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?  去我的?  黑金刚?\N{\rEnglish}What? Screw me, Tyrone?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.04,1:01:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去我的?!\N{\rEnglish}Screw me?!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.14,1:01:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  别激动...\N{\rEnglish}Wait a minute, all right? Just relax...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.78,1:01:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干的好  大老粗\N{\rEnglish}That's right, tough guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.45,1:01:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱莉  宝贝  快拿枪\N{\rEnglish}Julie, baby, get the gun!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.89,1:01:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快捡起枪\N{\rEnglish}Pick up that gun!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.43,1:01:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快射他  朝他的脸开枪\N{\rEnglish}Now, shoot him! Shoot him right in the face, Julie!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.26,1:01:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝他的脸开枪  快拿枪\N{\rEnglish}Shoot him right in the face! Get the gun!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.66,1:01:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿枪啊\N{\rEnglish}Get the gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.47,1:01:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛  你疯了?\N{\rEnglish}What, are you crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.67,1:01:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛?\N{\rEnglish}What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.40,1:01:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手\N{\rEnglish}Come on, now!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.27,1:01:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦斯  你有手铐吗?\N{\rEnglish}Max, you got cuffs?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.71,1:01:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有\N{\rEnglish}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.08,1:01:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\rEnglish}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.75,1:01:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个蠢贱货\N{\rEnglish}You stupid bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.15,1:01:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为你海扁我\N{\rEnglish}That's for beating the shit out of me!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.02,1:02:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为你混蛋透顶\N{\rEnglish}And that's for being an asshole!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.33,1:02:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个呢?\N{\rEnglish}And this?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.53,1:02:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为你叫我贱货\N{\rEnglish}This is for calling me a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.80,1:02:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊\N{\rEnglish}I felt that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.54,1:02:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再当你的芭比娃娃了\N{\rEnglish}And I'm not going to go your Barbie anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.91,1:02:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶  宝贝\N{\rEnglish}Goddamn, baby!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.38,1:02:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是又辣又带劲\N{\rEnglish}All that ass and muscles to go with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.78,1:02:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你不是金发妞\N{\rEnglish}I knew damn well you wasn't no blond.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.13,1:02:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来\N{\rEnglish}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.34,1:02:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩个  走吧\N{\rEnglish}Let's go, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.68,1:02:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样\N{\rEnglish}Whatever happens,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.88,1:02:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你知道一切会很顺利\N{\rEnglish}I want you to know everything's going to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.91,1:03:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂吗?\N{\rEnglish}Understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.71,1:03:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂\N{\rEnglish}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.72,1:03:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心\N{\rEnglish}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.45,1:03:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.79,1:03:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别瞎操心\N{\rEnglish}Don't worry about anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.25,1:03:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会永远在你身边\N{\rEnglish}I'll always be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.49,1:03:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开枪\N{\rEnglish}Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.33,1:03:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要释放人质  别开枪\N{\rEnglish}I'm letting some hostages go! Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.10,1:03:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  你们俩个\N{\rEnglish}All right, you two.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.71,1:03:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  你们俩个\N{\rEnglish}Let's go, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.97,1:03:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  谢谢你\N{\rEnglish}Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.41,1:03:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  萝莎  你也是\N{\rEnglish}All right, all right. Rose, you too.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.92,1:03:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  好好照顾小孩\N{\rEnglish}All right, Take care of the baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.75,1:03:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,持枪暴徒刚刚放了几个人质...\N{\rEnglish}The gunman has just freed several hostages...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.45,1:03:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们将会接受专案小组讯问\N{\rEnglish}who will be debriefed by the crisis team.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.16,1:03:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰老Q能帮小孩弄到心脏吗?\N{\rEnglish}Will John Q. Get a heart for his little boy?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.69,1:03:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间会证明一切  记者在医院...\N{\rEnglish}Only time will tell. From Hope Memorial Hospital...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.40,1:03:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,持枪暴徒掌控急诊室之后\N{\rEnglish}Is it true a gunshot victim was dropped off.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.70,1:03:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是否真有枪伤病患被送进去?\N{\rEnglish}After the gunman took over the E.R?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.27,1:03:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对  他让他进去的\N{\rEnglish}Yes. He let him inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.67,1:03:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请说句话  先生\N{\rEnglish}Can you comment, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.11,1:04:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人伤的很重\N{\rEnglish}The man was critically injured.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.47,1:04:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不是他让他进去  他死定了\N{\rEnglish}If he hadn't let him in, he would've died.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.48,1:04:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太太  你还好吧?\N{\rEnglish}Ma'am. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.21,1:04:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很好  我们的孩子快诞生了\N{\rEnglish}Oh, yeah, I feel good. We're having a baby!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.15,1:04:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太太  你对持枪暴徒有何看法\N{\rEnglish}Ma'am, do you have any comments about the gunman?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.12,1:04:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰老Q  很好的人\N{\rEnglish}John Q., very good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.39,1:04:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,持枪暴徒?\N{\rEnglish}The gunman?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.49,1:04:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好的人\N{\rEnglish}Very good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.53,1:04:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面有摄影机\N{\rEnglish}They got a camera in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.47,1:04:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在看拍到的画面\N{\rEnglish}They're watching a video feed.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.30,1:04:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道?\N{\rEnglish}How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.07,1:04:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在看东西\N{\rEnglish}They're looking at something, Freddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.47,1:04:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能弄到吗?\N{\rEnglish}Can you get it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.44,1:04:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老大  他们有的我都弄得到\N{\rEnglish}Boss, if they got it, I can get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.31,1:04:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你让步  暴徒会充斥全国医院\N{\rEnglish}You give in, there'll be guns in every hospital in the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.51,1:04:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是只有他家小孩生病\N{\rEnglish}Do you think Mr. Archibald's the only one who has a sick child?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.45,1:04:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去爱滋病房看  整层楼都是\N{\rEnglish}Ever checked out the HIV ward? There's a whole floor of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.65,1:04:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人会生老病死  人生就是如此\N{\rEnglish}People get sick, they die, that's the way it goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.76,1:04:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都面临这样的决策\N{\rEnglish}I face decisions like this every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.12,1:04:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人威胁要杀死无辜的人们\N{\rEnglish}A man's threatening to kill innocent people.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.86,1:04:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你不帮助他儿子\N{\rEnglish}Because you didn't help his son.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.90,1:04:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  这国家有五千万人\N{\rEnglish}There are 50 million people in this country.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.37,1:05:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有医疗保险\N{\rEnglish}Without medical insurance.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.67,1:05:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想改变这情况  去找国会议员\N{\rEnglish}If you'd like to change it, you should call your congressman.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.14,1:05:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\rEnglish}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.64,1:05:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何不告诉他  他儿子在名单上\N{\rEnglish}Why don't we just tell him his son's name's on the list?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.31,1:05:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是很好吗?\N{\rEnglish}I mean, doesn't that make sense?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.01,1:05:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他反正也不会知道真相\N{\rEnglish}How's he going to know, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.05,1:05:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官  抱歉  请你过来看看\N{\rEnglish}Sir? Pardon me, can you come take a look at this?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.65,1:05:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是皮华利  保安主管\N{\rEnglish}Sarge, Chief, this is Wally Pitoniak, head of security.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.06,1:05:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\rEnglish}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.69,1:05:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸会\N{\rEnglish}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.46,1:05:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你找到狙击点\N{\rEnglish}I got your spot.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.46,1:05:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里\N{\rEnglish}Here's your site.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.40,1:05:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里就是最好的点\N{\rEnglish}That's going to be your perch.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.10,1:05:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,X代表你的电话\N{\rEnglish}The X is your phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.40,1:05:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪只电话?\N{\rEnglish}Which phone?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.37,1:05:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠近一点\N{\rEnglish}Bring it up, Jeff.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.74,1:05:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里那只电话\N{\rEnglish}That phone right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.24,1:05:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  汤姆\N{\rEnglish}It is, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.21,1:05:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孟局长仍说会采取必要行动\N{\rEnglish}But Chief Monroe maintains that police will do what's necessary.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.22,1:05:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以确保人质的生命与安全\N{\rEnglish}to preserve the lives and safety of these hostages.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.12,1:05:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家\N{\rEnglish}This country, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.25,1:05:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管去到哪里\N{\rEnglish}Can't go anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.16,1:05:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都会被抢  被杀或是被刺\N{\rEnglish}Without getting mugged, or murdered, or stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.86,1:06:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子枪杀同学...\N{\rEnglish}Kids killing their classmates, drive-by...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.30,1:06:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至不敢再去邮局了\N{\rEnglish}I won't even go into a post office anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.80,1:06:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴  米区\N{\rEnglish}Shut up, Mitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.23,1:06:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才闭嘴\N{\rEnglish}You shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.50,1:06:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我恨那个混蛋  但他说的对\N{\rEnglish}I hate the bastard, but he's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.60,1:06:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道要弄到枪有多容易吗?\N{\rEnglish}You know how easy it is to get a gun?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.84,1:06:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五分钟  在枪展上...\N{\rEnglish}Five minutes, gun show...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.31,1:06:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你孩子病了\N{\rEnglish}I understand that your kid is sick, John.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.27,1:06:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这算什么  我也有人生啊\N{\rEnglish}But what makes him better than me? I get a life too.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.04,1:06:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对  但你有保险\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, but you got insurance.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.51,1:06:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要开枪?  你跟警察说的\N{\rEnglish}So you're going to shoot me? That's what you're telling the cops.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.15,1:06:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你儿子没得到心脏\N{\rEnglish}If your son doesn't the very first heart available.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.79,1:06:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就死定了\N{\rEnglish}We all die.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.79,1:06:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结局会怎样?\N{\rEnglish}How's it going to end, John?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.02,1:06:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么办?\N{\rEnglish}What's your move?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.16,1:06:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算怎样  我不知道\N{\rEnglish}I got no move, okay? I don't know what I'm going to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.73,1:06:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在等待奇迹  好吗?\N{\rEnglish}I'm waiting on a miracle, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.24,1:06:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在等待上帝的旨意\N{\rEnglish}I'm waiting on an act of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.86,1:07:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚契太太?\N{\rEnglish}Mrs. Archibald?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.50,1:07:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以谈谈吗?\N{\rEnglish}Could we have a word with you, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.60,1:07:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都是我的错\N{\rEnglish}This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.24,1:07:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医院告诉我要麦克出院时...\N{\rEnglish}When the hospital told me they were releasing Mikey...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.61,1:07:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打给约翰  对他乱吼\N{\rEnglish}I called John and I yelled at him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.64,1:07:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还叫他要采取行动\N{\rEnglish}And told him to do something, anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.01,1:07:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我没想到...\N{\rEnglish}But, I never thought...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.75,1:07:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白\N{\rEnglish}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.02,1:07:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有暴力倾向吗?\N{\rEnglish}Is he a violent man, Mrs. Archibald?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.49,1:07:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有  他温柔又亲切\N{\rEnglish}No, no, he's sweet and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.79,1:07:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他连小虫都不敢打\N{\rEnglish}He wouldn't hurt a fly.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.19,1:07:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可不这么说  他说要杀人\N{\rEnglish}That's not what he's saying. He's talking about killing people.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.40,1:07:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道的是我可能多心了...\N{\rEnglish}Now, what I want to know is...I may be fishing here...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.93,1:07:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是否在部队待过或什么的?\N{\rEnglish}but has he spent any time in the military or anything like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.27,1:07:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是在干嘛?\N{\rEnglish}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.24,1:07:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\rEnglish}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.34,1:07:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了\N{\rEnglish}I see what's going on here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.05,1:08:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想从我口中套话\N{\rEnglish}You want me to say something.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.38,1:08:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好让你拿来对付我丈夫\N{\rEnglish}That you can use against my husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.12,1:08:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的麻烦大了\N{\rEnglish}He's in a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.48,1:08:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要你去跟他谈谈\N{\rEnglish}And we're going to need you to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.62,1:08:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们把话说明白点吧\N{\rEnglish}Let's get something straight, mister.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.19,1:08:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能利用我去对付我丈夫\N{\rEnglish}You cannot use me to build a case against my husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.83,1:08:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我支持他所做的每一件事\N{\rEnglish}I support him in everything that he does.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.36,1:08:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我站在他那边  不是你这边\N{\rEnglish}I'm on his side, not yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.60,1:08:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚契太太\N{\rEnglish}Mrs. Archibald.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.36,1:08:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别跟我说话\N{\rEnglish}And you don't talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.34,1:08:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以说出我对你的看法...\N{\rEnglish}I would tell you what I think of you...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.01,1:08:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我是虔诚的教徒\N{\rEnglish}but I'm a Christian woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.18,1:08:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你们俩个离开\N{\rEnglish}Now, you two leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.61,1:08:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还要照顾我生病的孩子\N{\rEnglish}I have a sick child to look after.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.22,1:08:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已决定把麦克列入名单\N{\rEnglish}I've decided to put Michael on the recipient list.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.02,1:08:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医院会负担所有费用\N{\rEnglish}The hospital will pay for everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.43,1:08:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的?\N{\rEnglish}Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.33,1:08:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的\N{\rEnglish}Really.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.10,1:08:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\rEnglish}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.04,1:08:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊  谢谢你\N{\rEnglish}Oh, God, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.65,1:09:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真行\N{\rEnglish}You're good.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.98,1:09:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\rEnglish}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.38,1:09:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表演的真棒\N{\rEnglish}Quite the performance.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.02,1:09:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温暖的拥抱  诚挚的表情\N{\rEnglish}The comforting embrace, the sincere look.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.65,1:09:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一刹那  我真的相信你了\N{\rEnglish}For a minute, I actually believed that you cared.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.44,1:09:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记者塔克在希望纪念医院\N{\rEnglish}We go now to Hope Memorial Hospital live.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.67,1:09:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为您现场报导\N{\rEnglish}Tuck Lampley.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.51,1:09:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在医院前的群众越聚越多\N{\rEnglish}The crowd in front of Hope Memorial is growing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.51,1:09:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特勤小组已经到达现场\N{\rEnglish}The SWAT team has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.15,1:09:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现场情况变得相当紧张\N{\rEnglish}And the situation is becoming very tense.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.35,1:09:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在我身旁的是詹姆士·帕波\N{\rEnglish}Standing next to me is James Palumbo.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.35,1:09:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰·亚契的朋友\N{\rEnglish}Friend of John Archibald.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.22,1:09:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕波先生  谈谈亚契先生吧\N{\rEnglish}Mr. Palumbo, what can you tell us about John Archibald?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.82,1:09:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道...\N{\rEnglish}You know...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.36,1:09:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须诚实  塔克\N{\rEnglish}I got to be honest, Tuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.69,1:09:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这整件事真是可怕\N{\rEnglish}This whole thing sucks, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.83,1:10:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实这都是可以避免的\N{\rEnglish}It all could've been avoided so incredibly easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.97,1:10:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是约翰是富翁就不会这样\N{\rEnglish}None of this had to happen if John had been a millionaire.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.54,1:10:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是石油大亨就好 但他不了解\N{\rEnglish}Or, if his name was Rockefeller, but sometimes John don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.18,1:10:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这国家尊重的不是价值\N{\rEnglish}He don't understand that. What we hold sacred in this country isn't values.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.25,1:10:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是价钱\N{\rEnglish}It's value that's important.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.51,1:10:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有富人也有穷人\N{\rEnglish}We got haves, we got have-nots.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.65,1:10:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有白领  蓝领阶级  有失业的\N{\rEnglish}We got white-collar, blue-collar, and then we got no-collar.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.02,1:10:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以医院\N{\rEnglish}Inside there.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.59,1:10:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有豪华手术也有阳春手术...\N{\rEnglish}We got surgery, we got outpatient surgery...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.69,1:10:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有烂手术\N{\rEnglish}and we got out-of-luck surgery.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.46,1:10:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这社会有很多人\N{\rEnglish}There's a lot of people out there, Tuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.00,1:10:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多根本没有25万的人\N{\rEnglish}A lot of people here who don't got 250 grand.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.00,1:10:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这样的人逼到绝境真是可耻...\N{\rEnglish}To shame a man like that and back him into a corner...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.94,1:10:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来\N{\rEnglish}seems to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.67,1:10:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是社会制度失序\N{\rEnglish}Something is out of whack not someone.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.01,1:10:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂什么?  我只是个工人\N{\rEnglish}What do I know? I'm a factory worker.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.64,1:10:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得出来这事令你很难过...\N{\rEnglish}I can see this is making you very upset...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.58,1:10:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你若能面对镜头对约翰说话\N{\rEnglish}but, if you could speak to John Q. Right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.95,1:10:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要说什么?\N{\rEnglish}What would you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.32,1:10:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"詹姆士·帕波  约翰的友人"
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.39,1:10:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我与你同在  你要保重\N{\rEnglish}I'm there with you, and you take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.39,1:10:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个朋友的心声\N{\rEnglish}That's one man's opinion.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.49,1:10:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是记者塔克的报导\N{\rEnglish}Live at the crisis at Hope Memorial, this is Tuck Lampley.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.12,1:11:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?\N{\rEnglish}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.53,1:11:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副队长  人呢?\N{\rEnglish}Were is everybody?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.09,1:11:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要派人从通风管进去\N{\rEnglish}We're sending a guy in through the air duct.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.40,1:11:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是能让目标到这电话旁\N{\rEnglish}If we can get the target to this phone,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.07,1:11:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就能动手射杀他\N{\rEnglish}we got a clear shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.20,1:11:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?\N{\rEnglish}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.14,1:11:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  副队长  没错\N{\rEnglish}Yes, lieutenant, that is right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.71,1:11:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就等你下令了  局长\N{\rEnglish}When you're ready, chief.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.38,1:11:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张  各位\N{\rEnglish}Don't be nervous, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.35,1:11:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老孟\N{\rEnglish}Monroe!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.72,1:12:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老婆要开骂了\N{\rEnglish}My wife's calling.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.09,1:12:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更糟  是老爸要训话了\N{\rEnglish}Worse, chief, it's Father Time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.19,1:12:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我过来\N{\rEnglish}Come over here!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.46,1:12:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说了  法兰  我不想听...\N{\rEnglish}Not one word, Frank. Not one word, I don't want to hear...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.26,1:12:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋  在我背后搞小动作\N{\rEnglish}You son of bitch! You're going behind my back!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.47,1:12:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我怎么办?  你看看时间\N{\rEnglish}What do you want from me, Frank? Look at the clock!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.84,1:12:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你的表\N{\rEnglish}Look at your watch!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.20,1:12:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙说一刻钟后就要开杀戒...\N{\rEnglish}The guy said at a quarter after, he's going o start killing peple...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.37,1:12:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太愚蠢了\N{\rEnglish}This is so goddamn stupid!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.24,1:12:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你有什么好主意?\N{\rEnglish}Then, what's your great idea?!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.78,1:12:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好主意  特别是这个\N{\rEnglish}There are no great ideas, especially this!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.31,1:12:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有机会逮这家伙  我要动手\N{\rEnglish}I got a shot at this guy, and I'm going to take it!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.65,1:12:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做事老是不明快  你在说什么\N{\rEnglish}You always take the open shot! What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.25,1:12:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他老婆同意要跟他谈  让她来\N{\rEnglish}The wife has agreed to speak to him! Let her talk him down.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.39,1:12:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正打算这么做\N{\rEnglish}That's exactly what I'm going to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.79,1:12:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用他老婆逮他?\N{\rEnglish}Use the man's wife to set him up?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.39,1:12:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么有用我就用什么\N{\rEnglish}I'll use whatever work, Frnak.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.83,1:12:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你描绘一下吧\N{\rEnglish}Let me paint a picture for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.33,1:12:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个双输的局面\N{\rEnglish}Ok, what we have here is a lose/lose.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.47,1:12:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是他开始杀人质  就糟了\N{\rEnglish}If he starts whacking hostages, it's bad!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.37,1:12:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们若向他投降  也很糟\N{\rEnglish}And if we give in to this asshole it's also bad!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.00,1:12:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对谁很糟?\N{\rEnglish}Bad for who?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.94,1:12:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对大家都很糟  你  我  大家\N{\rEnglish}It's bad for everybody! Me, you, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.67,1:12:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年是选举年  就是很糟\N{\rEnglish}It's an election year, it's just bad!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.41,1:12:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样  这家伙不能成功\N{\rEnglish}However it goes down, Frank, this guy's not going to make it!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.58,1:13:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要杀他?  为选举铺路?\N{\rEnglish}So you kill him? That's a P.R. Bonanza, right?!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.85,1:13:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死一个坏蛋没什么\N{\rEnglish}I can live with one dead bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.85,1:13:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忍受不了的是\N{\rEnglish}What I can't live with.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.52,1:13:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有无辜的市民受伤\N{\rEnglish}Is one innocent person being hurt!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.15,1:13:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能在我任内\N{\rEnglish}Not one! Not on my watch!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.66,1:13:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法兰  你出局了\N{\rEnglish}You know what, Frank? You're out!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.59,1:13:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出局了?\N{\rEnglish}I'm out?!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.69,1:13:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与个人无关  但你被停职了\N{\rEnglish}No hard feelings, but you're relieved of duty.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.53,1:13:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起由我主导\N{\rEnglish}I'll handle this now.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.93,1:13:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你?\N{\rEnglish}You?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.90,1:13:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对  我\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.00,1:13:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我这是第一次指挥?\N{\rEnglish}Think it's my first time in the dance floor?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.80,1:13:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我是怎么得到这些的?\N{\rEnglish}How do you think I got these?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.94,1:13:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点  别惹我\N{\rEnglish}And watch it! Just watch it!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.44,1:13:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我承受很多压力  很多人在看\N{\rEnglish}I got a lot of pressure on me, Frank. A lot of eye's watching.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.64,1:13:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总要有人行动  而你不行动\N{\rEnglish}Someone's got to make the call. You're not going to do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.78,1:13:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就由我来\N{\rEnglish}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.95,1:13:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些人质怎么办?\N{\rEnglish}What about the hostages, the human beings?!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.55,1:13:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们最好小心点\N{\rEnglish}Better keep their heads down.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.80,1:13:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\N{\rEnglish}Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.76,1:13:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?\N{\rEnglish}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.57,1:13:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空调停了\N{\rEnglish}The air-conditioning just turned off.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.14,1:14:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就靠你了  别让我失望\N{\rEnglish}I'm counting on you, don't let me down.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.81,1:14:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再打电话给你\N{\rEnglish}I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.41,1:14:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶  借过\N{\rEnglish}Right on. Excuse me.
