Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.54,1:23:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别为难我了  我搞砸了\N{\rEnglish}Don't start breaking my balls. I screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.44,1:23:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你帮忙\N{\rEnglish}I need you to say my ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.85,1:23:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我搞砸了  求求你  法兰\N{\rEnglish}I stepped in shit. Lease, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.35,1:23:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  我请你吃牛排吧\N{\rEnglish}Come on. I'll buy you a steak.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.92,1:23:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北京烤鸭\N{\rEnglish}Peking duck.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.39,1:23:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  没问题\N{\rEnglish}You got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.89,1:23:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\rEnglish}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.02,1:23:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚洲的亚  契约的契\N{\rEnglish}A-R-C-H-l-B-A-L-D.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.86,1:23:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就把资料传给你\N{\rEnglish}I'm faxing you all the stuff right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.41,1:24:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  来吧  快把这事解决\N{\rEnglish}Okay, come on in. Let's clear this up.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.41,1:24:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开火\N{\rEnglish}Hold your fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.94,1:24:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开火  把枪放下  放下\N{\rEnglish}Don't fire. Turn them down. Turn them down.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.11,1:24:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有很多摄影机  别做傻事\N{\rEnglish}There's a lot of cameras. I don't want anybody doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.32,1:24:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你来的是谁?\N{\rEnglish}Who's that with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.59,1:24:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穆警官\N{\rEnglish}Sergeant Moody.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.15,1:24:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察局的孟局长\N{\rEnglish}Police Chief Monroe.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.76,1:24:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事  约翰?\N{\rEnglish}What's going on here, John?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.13,1:24:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没穿裤子\N{\rEnglish}He's got no pants on.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.84,1:24:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你骗我  副队长\N{\rEnglish}You lied to me, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.18,1:24:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说你会给我回报  但你没有\N{\rEnglish}You said you'd call back, Frank, but you didn't call.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.28,1:24:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我放了人质给你\N{\rEnglish}I give you your hostages.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.75,1:24:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你却没给我回报\N{\rEnglish}But you didn't call me back. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.98,1:24:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你要我死\N{\rEnglish}Because you want me dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.52,1:24:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人想要你死  约翰\N{\rEnglish}Nobody wants to kill you, John.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.29,1:24:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人想要我死?\N{\rEnglish}Nobody wants to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.05,1:24:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\rEnglish}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.45,1:24:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有?\N{\rEnglish}Nobody?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.02,1:24:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\rEnglish}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.62,1:24:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人也不想?  他也不想?\N{\rEnglish}None if these guys? Not him?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.62,1:24:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想\N{\rEnglish}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.29,1:24:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  那这是什么\N{\rEnglish}Okay, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.23,1:24:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?\N{\rEnglish}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.83,1:25:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为情况会变成怎样?\N{\rEnglish}What did you think would happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.77,1:25:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道实情?  这就是实情\N{\rEnglish}You want truth? Here's some truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.71,1:25:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情终将会对你不利的\N{\rEnglish}This is going to end bad for you, John.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.67,1:25:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只有两条出路\N{\rEnglish}There's only two ways out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.91,1:25:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去坐牢...\N{\rEnglish}Jail...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.91,1:25:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是没命\N{\rEnglish}or dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.61,1:25:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我儿子病的很重\N{\rEnglish}My son is very sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.62,1:25:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他需要人帮忙\N{\rEnglish}And he needs some help.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.62,1:25:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白\N{\rEnglish}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.89,1:25:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这年头做人很难\N{\rEnglish}It's hard to be a man these days.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.85,1:25:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很难知道该怎么做才对\N{\rEnglish}Hard to know what the right thing is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.32,1:25:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但请你放下枪\N{\rEnglish}But put the gun, John.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.69,1:25:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没听我说  我儿子病了\N{\rEnglish}You're not hearing me, Frank! My son is sick!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.90,1:25:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  没别的了\N{\rEnglish}That's it! There's nothing else!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.43,1:25:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结束\N{\rEnglish}End of story!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.13,1:25:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们生病  就需要帮忙\N{\rEnglish}When people are sick, they deserve a little help.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.30,1:25:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶\N{\rEnglish}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.14,1:25:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生病  帮忙\N{\rEnglish}Sick, Help!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.87,1:25:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生病  帮忙\N{\rEnglish}Sick, Help!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.98,1:25:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算帮我儿子送葬\N{\rEnglish}I am not going to bury my son!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.35,1:25:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我儿子才会帮我送葬\N{\rEnglish}My son is going to bury me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.99,1:25:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这些人在乎你?  才不呢\N{\rEnglish}You think these people give a shit about you? They don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.86,1:25:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是暂时的新闻焦点\N{\rEnglish}You're the cause if the moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.79,1:26:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人在乎  这才是事实\N{\rEnglish}Nobody cares, John. That's the real truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.69,1:26:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人在乎  只有你在乎\N{\rEnglish}Nobody cares. Only you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.33,1:26:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你跟我...\N{\rEnglish}And it's only you and out here...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.20,1:26:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有这些指着你的枪\N{\rEnglish}and all these guns pointed at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.84,1:26:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么做?  由你决定\N{\rEnglish}So, what do you want to do? It's your call.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.47,1:26:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要我儿子\N{\rEnglish}I want my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.21,1:26:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要我儿子进来陪我\N{\rEnglish}I want my son inside with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.18,1:26:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\rEnglish}Can't do it, John.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.68,1:26:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我儿子送来  我就放了枪手\N{\rEnglish}You give my boy, I give you your sniper.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.65,1:26:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切就结束\N{\rEnglish}Then it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.82,1:26:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我儿子送来...\N{\rEnglish}You bring my son...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.39,1:26:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我投降\N{\rEnglish}I give up.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.96,1:26:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都回家\N{\rEnglish}everybody goes home.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.50,1:26:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都平安无事\N{\rEnglish}Everybody's safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.07,1:26:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我儿子送来\N{\rEnglish}You bring me my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.01,1:26:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\rEnglish}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.64,1:26:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\rEnglish}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.48,1:26:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得如何?\N{\rEnglish}What do you think, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.38,1:26:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想就送给他吧\N{\rEnglish}I say give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.55,1:26:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他儿子进去  他就不会杀人\N{\rEnglish}He won't hurt anybody with his boy in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.25,1:26:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要救人质  不是送人质\N{\rEnglish}The object is get hostages out, not to bring them in.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.65,1:27:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是人质  那是他儿子\N{\rEnglish}It's not a hostage. It's his son.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.46,1:27:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人都没看过新闻吗?\N{\rEnglish}Have all these people been on the new?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.06,1:27:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你的了  法兰\N{\rEnglish}It's your call, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.63,1:27:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.23,1:27:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  把他送进去\N{\rEnglish}All right, give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.04,1:27:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停  不行\N{\rEnglish}Hold it. No-N-No.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.87,1:27:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是他母亲  我要跟着去\N{\rEnglish}I'm his mother. I need to be in there!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.81,1:27:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别过来  停\N{\rEnglish}Stop right there. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.75,1:27:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走开  快走开\N{\rEnglish}Go. Beat it. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.75,1:27:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快  快\N{\rEnglish}Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.67,1:27:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦大了  约翰\N{\rEnglish}We're in trouble, John.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.07,1:27:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克的血压降到四十几了\N{\rEnglish}Mike's blood pressure's dropped into the mid-40's.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.64,1:27:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心房血压应该只有十几\N{\rEnglish}His atrial blood pressure should be in the low teens.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.51,1:27:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是35\N{\rEnglish}It's 35.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.64,1:27:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  约翰\N{\rEnglish}I'm sorry, John.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.01,1:27:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有新的心脏...\N{\rEnglish}Without a new heart...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.44,1:28:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是活不了的\N{\rEnglish}he's not going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.58,1:28:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.89,1:28:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就用我的\N{\rEnglish}You take mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.06,1:28:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\rEnglish}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.86,1:28:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听见了\N{\rEnglish}You heard me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.99,1:28:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿我的心脏给麦克用\N{\rEnglish}Take my heart and you put it in Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.89,1:28:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老兄  你真是疯了\N{\rEnglish}Man, you done lost your damn mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.60,1:28:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是认真的吧\N{\rEnglish}You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.50,1:28:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是认真的  我很认真\N{\rEnglish}You bet I'm serious. I'm dead serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.97,1:28:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天爷\N{\rEnglish}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.03,1:28:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那意味着你会死\N{\rEnglish}That means you'll be dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.80,1:28:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我儿子会活\N{\rEnglish}And my son will live.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.14,1:28:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能这么做\N{\rEnglish}You can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.11,1:28:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是唯一的方法\N{\rEnglish}It's the only way.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.94,1:28:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不懂  生理上你不能这么做\N{\rEnglish}No, physically, you can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.08,1:28:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以  我杀了自己\N{\rEnglish}Yes, I can. I kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.68,1:28:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剖开我  拿走心脏  很完美\N{\rEnglish}You open me up, you take my heart. It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.38,1:28:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天  这疯狂了\N{\rEnglish}Man, that's just crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.78,1:28:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能这样就把你的心移给麦克\N{\rEnglish}No, we can't just remove your heart and put it in Michael's body.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.45,1:28:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多未知因素\N{\rEnglish}Too many unknowns.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.89,1:28:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捐赠者跟受赠者的比对程序复杂\N{\rEnglish}Matching a donor and a recipient is complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.92,1:28:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多重要的检验要做\N{\rEnglish}There are critical tests to be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.76,1:28:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比方说呢?\N{\rEnglish}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.42,1:28:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,互相比对血型  胸腔大小\N{\rEnglish}Cross-matches for blood type, chest cavity measurements.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.69,1:28:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是血型不符\N{\rEnglish}If both blood tissues are not compatible.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.00,1:28:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都知道  我们仔细比对过\N{\rEnglish}I know all about compatibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.00,1:28:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是B型阳性  组织吻合...\N{\rEnglish}We're both B-positive, our tissues match...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.20,1:28:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他心脏比正常大三倍 我的可以\N{\rEnglish}his heart's three times the size of a normal, so will fit.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.27,1:29:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我们很合\N{\rEnglish}You know we're compatible.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.77,1:29:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是不可能的\N{\rEnglish}It's out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.27,1:29:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生  我说可以\N{\rEnglish}Doc, I'm telling you he will make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.64,1:29:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  约翰  不行\N{\rEnglish}Can't do it. John. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.35,1:29:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我死了\N{\rEnglish}So if I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.75,1:29:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也不会拿我的心去救他?\N{\rEnglish}You're not going to take heart and save his life?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.75,1:29:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你宁可让两个人死也不动手?\N{\rEnglish}You'll let two people die instead of one because of a technicality?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.29,1:29:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为约翰是对的\N{\rEnglish}I think what John is trying to do is right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.62,1:29:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为他很勇敢\N{\rEnglish}I think it's so brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.59,1:29:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克会想要吗?  你太太呢?\N{\rEnglish}What do you think Mike would want? What about your wife?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.06,1:29:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克还小  他不懂什么对他好\N{\rEnglish}Mike's too young to know what's good for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.46,1:29:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是他父亲  我有责任保护他\N{\rEnglish}I'm his father. It's my job to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.36,1:29:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何况  狄妮也会做一样的事\N{\rEnglish}Besides, Denise would do the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.70,1:29:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰  听着\N{\rEnglish}John, look.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.03,1:29:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道麦克的情况很不好\N{\rEnglish}I know what's happening to Mike is bad, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.04,1:29:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上  根本就很糟\N{\rEnglish}Matter of fact, it's the worst.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.74,1:29:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但自杀并不能解决事情\N{\rEnglish}But killing yourself ain't going to solve a damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.94,1:29:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时你必须放手\N{\rEnglish}Sometimes you just got to let go.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.08,1:29:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让上帝接手\N{\rEnglish}And let God.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.51,1:29:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受它吧  兄弟\N{\rEnglish}Just accept it, brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.15,1:29:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受它\N{\rEnglish}Accept it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.85,1:29:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受什么?\N{\rEnglish}Accept what?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.02,1:29:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受什么?\N{\rEnglish}Accept what?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.76,1:29:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克会死\N{\rEnglish}That Mike is going to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.86,1:29:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不接受\N{\rEnglish}No, I don't accept that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.90,1:29:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝不\N{\rEnglish}Ever!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.63,1:30:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不接受  听着\N{\rEnglish}No, I reject that out of hand. I mean, look.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.33,1:30:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他对你而言只是病人  我明白\N{\rEnglish}All right, he's a patient to you. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.90,1:30:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个好孩子\N{\rEnglish}He's a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.17,1:30:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他喜欢健身\N{\rEnglish}I mean, he loves bodybuilding.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.28,1:30:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想当健美先生  你相信吗?\N{\rEnglish}He wants to be a bodybuilder. Can you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.98,1:30:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也很幽默  你会喜欢他的\N{\rEnglish}And he's funny. You' d like him.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.22,1:30:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会喜欢他的  若你能认识他\N{\rEnglish}You'd like him, doc, if you got to know him.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.32,1:30:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是很喜欢他\N{\rEnglish}I do like him. All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.45,1:30:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就求求你  我求你\N{\rEnglish}Then please, I'm just begging you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.99,1:30:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别管那些规定了\N{\rEnglish}Step outside the rules.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.09,1:30:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想  我真的很想\N{\rEnglish}I'd like to, John. I really would.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.32,1:30:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你的请求太过份了\N{\rEnglish}But what you're asking crosses the line.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.56,1:30:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这完全是不道德的\N{\rEnglish}It is completely unethical.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.90,1:30:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太过份?  你才太过份了\N{\rEnglish}I'm crossing he line? You're crossing the line.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.30,1:30:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整个制度都太过份了  谁在乎\N{\rEnglish}The whole system crossing the line. Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.20,1:30:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你不明白我在说什么\N{\rEnglish}Maybe you don' understand what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.07,1:30:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎  我儿子要活下去\N{\rEnglish}I don't give a damn. My son's going to live.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.11,1:30:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你还没搞清楚\N{\rEnglish}Maybe you haven't figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.91,1:30:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽一切力量让他活下去\N{\rEnglish}I'll do whatever I got to do for him to live.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.78,1:30:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你打算怎么办?\N{\rEnglish}So, what are you going to do?
