Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.95,1:30:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会自杀\N{\rEnglish}I'll kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.62,1:30:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗?\N{\rEnglish}All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.09,1:30:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看事情会怎么样\N{\rEnglish}Let's just see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.19,1:31:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就是这样吗?  他需要捐赠人\N{\rEnglish}That's what this is all about, right? He needs donate
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.06,1:31:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总要有人死  好让他活\N{\rEnglish}Somebody's got to die in order for him to live.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.86,1:31:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是他父亲  就是我了\N{\rEnglish}I'm his father. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.24,1:31:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\rEnglish}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.68,1:31:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧?  好什么?\N{\rEnglish}All right? All right what?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.44,1:31:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要我动手就动手吧\N{\rEnglish}I'll do it if that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.81,1:31:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说你要让他自杀?\N{\rEnglish}You'll let him kill himself?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.35,1:31:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他若死了  有何不可?\N{\rEnglish}Once he's dead, why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.55,1:31:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我认识最好的外科医生\N{\rEnglish}You are the finest surgeon I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.19,1:31:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能为这人搞砸你的事业\N{\rEnglish}You cannot throw your career away for this man.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.79,1:31:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生  你动手就完了\N{\rEnglish}Doctor, if you do this, you're finished.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.09,1:31:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会怎样?  告我吗?\N{\rEnglish}What are they going to do? Sue me?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.13,1:31:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吊销执照?\N{\rEnglish}Disbar me?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.26,1:31:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我赶出俱乐部\N{\rEnglish}Evict me from the country club?
