Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.80,1:33:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是O型  我发誓\N{\rEnglish}No, no, no. Type O, swear to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.87,1:34:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\rEnglish}Thank you.
