Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.76,1:34:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等着上报吧\N{\rEnglish}See you in the funny papers.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.70,1:34:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能跟他谈谈吗?\N{\rEnglish}Can I have a word with him?
