Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.18,1:35:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你帮我弄到新的心脏了?\N{\rEnglish}Did you bring me a new heart?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.62,1:35:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  弄到了\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, we got you one.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.03,1:35:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是命中有贵人\N{\rEnglish}I guess you got a guardian angel.
