Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.71,1:41:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的吗?\N{\rEnglish}Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.64,1:41:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞机刚降落在芝加哥机场\N{\rEnglish}The Learjet just landed at O'Hare.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.21,1:41:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直升机15分钟内就送到了\N{\rEnglish}The helicopter will be here in 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.85,1:41:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这荣耀归你  好吗?\N{\rEnglish}You do the honors, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.45,1:41:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  说吧\N{\rEnglish}Okay, go?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.82,1:41:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰  是我\N{\rEnglish}John, baby, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.62,1:41:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰\N{\rEnglish}John.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.96,1:41:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这没用  约翰?\N{\rEnglish}It's not working. John?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.76,1:41:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  接起来  约翰...\N{\rEnglish}Please, baby, pick up! John, can you...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.24,1:41:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰\N{\rEnglish}John.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.69,1:42:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰  这是奇迹  有心脏了\N{\rEnglish}John! It's a miracle, baby! They found a heart!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.92,1:42:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰  这是奇迹  有心脏了\N{\rEnglish}John, it's a miracle! They found a heart!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.49,1:42:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心脏送到了\N{\rEnglish}The heart is here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.13,1:42:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重覆  小麦克的心脏送来了\N{\rEnglish}I repeat, the heart for little Mike Archibald has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.40,1:42:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这真是个不可思议的结局\N{\rEnglish}What an unbelievable ending to this incredible, tumultuous day.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.37,1:42:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了\N{\rEnglish}Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.48,1:42:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错  人质们陆续出来了\N{\rEnglish}Yes, the hostages are coming out.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.41,1:42:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个  两个...\N{\rEnglish}One, two...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.15,1:42:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们历经痛苦折磨似乎累坏了\N{\rEnglish}They appear to be exhausted from what must've been an excruciating ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.78,1:42:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出来更多人了  挥着手\N{\rEnglish}More coming out. Hands waved in the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.09,1:42:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自由  终于自由了\N{\rEnglish}Freedom, freedom at last.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.79,1:42:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方护送他们到安全的地方\N{\rEnglish}The police are escorting them to safety.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.66,1:42:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们有什么感觉?\N{\rEnglish}How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.73,1:42:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都出来了  这是约翰\N{\rEnglish}Somebody else is coming. It's John Q.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.03,1:42:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰出来了  他高举双手\N{\rEnglish}John Q has come out, hand in the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.17,1:42:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把枪放下了  似乎要投降\N{\rEnglish}He's putting the gun down. He appears to be surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.74,1:42:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干的好  约翰\N{\rEnglish}Way to go, John!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.84,1:42:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方小心的接近他\N{\rEnglish}The police are approaching.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.68,1:42:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们逮住他了  他们压制了约翰\N{\rEnglish}And they've got him. They've subdued John Q.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.28,1:43:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铐上手铐  一切似乎结束了\N{\rEnglish}The handcuffs are on and it appears to be over.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.01,1:43:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全落幕了\N{\rEnglish}It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.15,1:43:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若说画面能代表千言万语\N{\rEnglish}If pictures speak a thousand words.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.69,1:43:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些影像更能令人感受到震撼\N{\rEnglish}Then these images do speak volumes.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.39,1:43:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在  事件落幕  提醒您...\N{\rEnglish}And now, as the bloody standoff comes to an end, we remind you...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.06,1:43:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第八频道是第一个\N{\rEnglish}that channel eight was here first,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.23,1:43:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,独家赶到现场连线报导的频道...\N{\rEnglish}with moment-to-moment live coverage...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.47,1:43:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是希望纪念医院的危机报导\N{\rEnglish}of "crisis at Hope Memorial."
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.77,1:43:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是蓝塔克\N{\rEnglish}I'm Tuck Lampley.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.65,1:43:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门\N{\rEnglish}Open those doors!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.55,1:43:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点\N{\rEnglish}Coming through.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.19,1:43:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们爱你  约翰\N{\rEnglish}We love you, John!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.49,1:43:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝保佑你  我也会这么做的\N{\rEnglish}God bless you, John! I'd do the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.16,1:43:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油  约翰\N{\rEnglish}Go, John!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.02,1:44:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心脏\N{\rEnglish}Heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.39,1:44:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\rEnglish}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.16,1:44:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长剪\N{\rEnglish}Metzenbaums.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.54,1:44:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很衰弱\N{\rEnglish}He's hypostenic.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.90,1:44:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\rEnglish}Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.45,1:44:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为我戴上它们吧  可以吗?\N{\rEnglish}Put these on for, would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.22,1:44:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来\N{\rEnglish}Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.40,1:45:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉起来\N{\rEnglish}Life it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.47,1:45:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.07,1:45:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了\N{\rEnglish}Done.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.28,1:45:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,升高血压\N{\rEnglish}Pressure up.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.31,1:45:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,升高血压\N{\rEnglish}Pressure up.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.01,1:45:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  三\N{\rEnglish}One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.09,1:45:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了\N{\rEnglish}It worked!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.29,1:45:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了  约翰  成功了\N{\rEnglish}It worked, John! It worked!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.64,1:45:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是一桩案例...\N{\rEnglish}The other big story...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.87,1:45:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰被控绑架与企图谋杀\N{\rEnglish}John Q goes on trial today for kidnapping and attempted murder charges.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.94,1:45:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全因为HMO拒绝给付\N{\rEnglish}All because an HMO denied coverage
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.65,1:45:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他儿子的心脏移植手术\N{\rEnglish}For his son's heart transplant.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.31,1:45:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未来更糟  HMO会拒绝承保\N{\rEnglish}It'll be more expensive for you, HMO's, to deny coverage when people need it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.65,1:45:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有四千万美国人没有保险\N{\rEnglish}There are still 40 million Americans who are uninsured.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.09,1:46:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚  约翰·亚契的审判继续着\N{\rEnglish}Tonight, as the trial continues, John Quincy Archibald:
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.76,1:46:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是坏蛋还是好父亲?\N{\rEnglish}Vigilante or heroic father?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.00,1:46:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来决定\N{\rEnglish}You decide.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.40,1:46:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告垮他们  好让他们知道...\N{\rEnglish}Sue the pants off them for millions of dollars to let them know...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.23,1:46:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们早知道这个健保系统很烂\N{\rEnglish}We've know for years that this is a crappy health care system.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.04,1:46:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府根本不在乎我们\N{\rEnglish}The government don't care about us.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.78,1:46:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想约翰用的是信心健保计划\N{\rEnglish}I guess John Q was using one of those faith-bassed health care plans.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.45,1:46:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只能祈祷  政府才不管你\N{\rEnglish}That's where you just pray, and the government does nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.52,1:46:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重点是我们的敌人\N{\rEnglish}The point is that the enemy
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.35,1:46:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是我们自己\N{\rEnglish}That we're trying to identify is us.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.89,1:46:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那才是重点\N{\rEnglish}That's the point.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.05,1:46:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们才是终结健保系统的人\N{\rEnglish}We are the ones who shot down national health care.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.09,1:46:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（三个月后）
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.03,1:46:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不希望税金提高\N{\rEnglish}We are the ones who don't want our taxes raised.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.93,1:46:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们必须仔细审视这个问题\N{\rEnglish}You have to look in the mirror for this problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.93,1:46:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退后  拜托  退后\N{\rEnglish}Back up. Come on, back up.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.30,1:46:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就回答一个问题吧\N{\rEnglish}Just one question, please!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.47,1:46:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退后\N{\rEnglish}Back up.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.91,1:46:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开  走吧\N{\rEnglish}Out of the way. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.05,1:47:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在有何感觉  约翰?\N{\rEnglish}How are you feeling right now, John?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.42,1:47:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪审团是否已达成判决?\N{\rEnglish}Has the jury reached a verdict?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.73,1:47:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  庭上\N{\rEnglish}We have, Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.77,1:47:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一项罪名  蓄意谋杀...\N{\rEnglish}As to count one: Attempted murder...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.84,1:47:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们认为被告  约翰·亚契...\N{\rEnglish}we find the defendant, John Quincy Archibald...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.64,1:47:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无罪\N{\rEnglish}not quilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.05,1:47:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请安静\N{\rEnglish}Quiet, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.62,1:47:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二项罪名\N{\rEnglish}On count two:
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.32,1:47:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非法持械攻击...\N{\rEnglish}Armed criminal action...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.89,1:47:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无罪\N{\rEnglish}not quilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.19,1:47:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安静\N{\rEnglish}Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.39,1:47:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后一项罪名\N{\rEnglish}On the final count:
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.29,1:47:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绑架并囚禁毕朱莉...\N{\rEnglish}The kidnapping and false imprisonment of Julie Byrd...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.40,1:47:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯麦斯  冈萝莎...\N{\rEnglish}Max Conlan, Rosa Gonzalez...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.87,1:47:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾伦克莱医生...\N{\rEnglish}Dr. Ellen Klein...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.20,1:47:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马莱斯  麦史提...\N{\rEnglish}Lester Matthews, Steve Maguire...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.01,1:47:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,施蜜丽和施史提...\N{\rEnglish}Miriam and Steve Smith...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.68,1:48:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷透纳医生...\N{\rEnglish}Dr. Raymond Turner...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.95,1:48:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昆米区  欧黛比...\N{\rEnglish}Mitch Quigley, Debby Utley...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.12,1:48:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们认为被告...\N{\rEnglish}we find the defendant...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.09,1:48:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有罪\N{\rEnglish}guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.89,1:48:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请安静\N{\rEnglish}Quiet, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.29,1:48:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一周后宣判\N{\rEnglish}Sentencing will be one week from today.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.93,1:48:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体起立\N{\rEnglish}All rise.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.50,1:48:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会得到什么处罚?\N{\rEnglish}So, what are we looking at?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.27,1:48:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会坐一阵子牢\N{\rEnglish}Well, he's going to do some time.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.44,1:48:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法官不会判他超过三到五年\N{\rEnglish}The judge is not going to give him more than three to five,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.17,1:48:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会设法降到两年\N{\rEnglish}I'll try for two.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.27,1:48:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉\N{\rEnglish}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.45,1:48:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧  大强棒?\N{\rEnglish}You all right, slugger?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.48,1:48:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\rEnglish}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.78,1:48:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好照顾你妈\N{\rEnglish}Take good care of your mother, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.95,1:48:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在是家里唯一的男人了\N{\rEnglish}You're the man of the house now.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.02,1:48:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有问题  吉米和吉娜会帮你\N{\rEnglish}Any problems, Jimmy and Gina will be here for you too.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.29,1:48:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.17,1:49:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以你为荣\N{\rEnglish}I'm so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.64,1:49:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他们瞧瞧你的厉害\N{\rEnglish}Give them frigging hell, Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.18,1:49:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都别担心了\N{\rEnglish}Don't worry about nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.58,1:49:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸?\N{\rEnglish}Hey, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.98,1:49:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见\N{\rEnglish}Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.05,1:49:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是再见  儿子\N{\rEnglish}It's not goodbye, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.39,1:49:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回头见\N{\rEnglish}See you later.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.45,1:49:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰\N{\rEnglish}Hey, John!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.45,1:49:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保重  老兄\N{\rEnglish}Take care, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.42,1:49:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的英雄\N{\rEnglish}You're my hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.68,1:50:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸\N{\rEnglish}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.02,1:50:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\rEnglish}Thank you.

